00:01:51.440 --> 00:01:53.640 line:77% align:middle position:50% size:80%
(Girl narrates)
There used to be horses in that barn.

00:01:53.680 --> 00:01:56.400 line:77% align:middle position:50% size:80%
At least,
that's what my grandfather says.

00:01:57.760 --> 00:02:01.800 line:77% align:middle position:50% size:80%
We're probably the only horse farm
in Lexington, Kentucky,

00:02:01.840 --> 00:02:03.440 line:83% align:middle position:50% size:80%
that doesn't have one horse.

00:02:04.480 --> 00:02:05.920 line:83% align:middle position:50% size:80%
Not one.

00:02:05.960 --> 00:02:08.880 line:83% align:middle position:50% size:80%
( THUNDER RUMBLES IN DISTANCE )

00:02:23.120 --> 00:02:24.600 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
MAN: It might rain.

00:02:30.480 --> 00:02:34.200 line:77% align:right size:80% position:90%
Pat said it'd be a good day for me
to, er, come down to the diner.

00:02:34.240 --> 00:02:35.680 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
Yeah, whatever.

00:02:35.720 --> 00:02:38.160 line:77% align:right size:80% position:90%
It'll just be breakfast and lunch
three days a week.

00:02:38.200 --> 00:02:39.960 line:77% align:left position:16% size:64%
Well, if you're
working down the diner,

00:02:40.000 --> 00:02:42.560 line:77% align:left position:16% size:64%
she comes home from school
to nobody here.

00:02:42.600 --> 00:02:44.520 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
Well, Pop lives right next door.

00:02:46.880 --> 00:02:48.720 line:77% align:right size:80% position:90%
I mean, I know you two
don't talk much,

00:02:48.760 --> 00:02:50.680 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
but he and Cale get along real well.

00:02:51.680 --> 00:02:53.520 line:77% align:left position:16% size:64%
<c.black>..........................</c>And, er...
"And, er" what?

00:02:54.960 --> 00:02:56.600 line:77% align:right size:80% position:90%
You know you've been
promising her for months

00:02:56.640 --> 00:02:58.440 line:77% align:right size:80% position:90%
that you would
take her to work with you.

00:02:58.480 --> 00:03:01.480 line:77% align:left position:16% size:64%
And I will, Lil. But not today,
honey. I got a big race.

00:03:01.520 --> 00:03:04.760 line:77% align:left position:18% size:62%
What am I supposed to tell her?
<c.black>........</c>Tell her I was running late

00:03:04.800 --> 00:03:06.280 line:77% align:right size:80% position:90%
and I didn't have time
to wait for her.

00:03:07.280 --> 00:03:08.720 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
You tell her.

00:03:08.760 --> 00:03:10.240 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
Honey, I'm going to work.

00:03:20.520 --> 00:03:22.000 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
( DOOR SLAMS )

00:03:42.840 --> 00:03:45.000 line:77% align:right size:80% position:90%
Alright, get in.
I don't wanna be late.

00:03:55.800 --> 00:03:57.400 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
There you go.

00:05:08.200 --> 00:05:10.520 line:83% align:middle position:50% size:80%
( THUNDER RUMBLES )

00:05:23.560 --> 00:05:26.960 line:77% align:left position:18% size:62%
58 and 1.
<c.black>.....</c>MAN: Alright. Got ya.

00:05:28.280 --> 00:05:29.960 line:77% align:left position:16% size:64%
Alright, send Sonya.
Don't let her out.

00:05:30.040 --> 00:05:32.080 line:77% align:left position:16% size:64%
I just wanna...
just wanna watch her action.

00:05:34.040 --> 00:05:36.080 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
(Horse whinnies)

00:05:47.560 --> 00:05:49.000 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
I like him.

00:05:50.040 --> 00:05:51.680 line:83% align:middle position:50% size:80%
Her.

00:05:53.160 --> 00:05:54.840 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
I like her too.

00:05:56.960 --> 00:05:59.880 line:83% align:middle position:50% size:80%
( THUNDER RUMBLES )

00:06:04.240 --> 00:06:07.440 line:83% align:middle position:50% size:80%
( PEOPLE CHATTER, HORSES WHINNY )

00:06:07.520 --> 00:06:09.160 line:77% align:left position:16% size:64%
MAN: Can I get
a bucket of multigrain,

00:06:09.240 --> 00:06:10.800 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
stall number three, please?

00:06:12.160 --> 00:06:13.720 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
Good morning, sir.

00:06:13.800 --> 00:06:15.240 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
Good morning!

00:06:15.320 --> 00:06:17.040 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
Balon, remember Cale?

00:06:17.120 --> 00:06:19.240 line:77% align:left position:16% size:64%
Sure.
She doesn't come around anymore.

00:06:19.320 --> 00:06:21.400 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
Wow, honey, you gotten so big.

00:06:22.480 --> 00:06:24.400 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
Senorita, buenos dias.

00:06:24.480 --> 00:06:26.600 line:77% align:left position:16% size:64%
<c.black>.......</c>MR CRANE: Eddie,
let's take a look at...

00:06:26.680 --> 00:06:29.000 line:77% align:left position:18% size:62%
That means 'good morning'.
<c.black>.........................</c>Morning.

00:06:29.080 --> 00:06:31.440 line:77% align:right size:80% position:90%
He's got legs like steel.
Take him in.

00:06:33.560 --> 00:06:37.040 line:77% align:left position:16% size:64%
Whoa! Whoa, whoa. What have you
got there? Have you got some candy?

00:06:37.120 --> 00:06:39.800 line:77% align:left position:16% size:64%
<c.black>.........................</c>(Whinnies)
Hey, Sonya! There you go, Sonya.

00:06:39.880 --> 00:06:42.320 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
Ohh, yeah! That's Sonya.

00:06:42.400 --> 00:06:44.160 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
She likes candy.

00:06:44.240 --> 00:06:45.960 line:83% align:middle position:50% size:80%
Sonya likes Twizzlers.

00:06:46.040 --> 00:06:48.040 line:77% align:left position:22% size:58%
Yeah?
<c.black>.......................</c>Well...

00:06:49.080 --> 00:06:52.200 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
Who's this? Got a new jockey? Hey?

00:06:52.280 --> 00:06:53.880 line:83% align:middle position:50% size:80%
This is my daughter, Cale.

00:06:53.960 --> 00:06:56.000 line:83% align:left position:68% size:12%
Oh. Hey.

00:06:56.080 --> 00:07:00.040 line:77% align:right size:80% position:90%
I'm Manolin Vallarta,
the greatest jockey in the world.

00:07:00.120 --> 00:07:02.320 line:77% align:left position:16% size:64%
(Whispers)
Fattest jockey in the world.

00:07:02.400 --> 00:07:05.040 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
Ah! Muchacho, too tall to race.

00:07:05.120 --> 00:07:07.280 line:77% align:right size:80% position:90%
Look at you, man.
Look at these clothes.

00:07:07.360 --> 00:07:10.400 line:77% align:right size:80% position:90%
This is a barn, not a disco.
(Speaks Spanish)

00:07:12.640 --> 00:07:14.040 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
He likes the way I dress.

00:07:14.120 --> 00:07:15.640 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
(Chuckles)

00:07:15.720 --> 00:07:17.240 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
Now, you see your daddy?

00:07:17.320 --> 00:07:21.080 line:77% align:left position:16% size:64%
You see how he's feeling the legs?
You see that?

00:07:21.160 --> 00:07:24.120 line:77% align:left position:16% size:64%
Well, he just want to make sure
the horse is sound and healthy.

00:07:24.200 --> 00:07:26.600 line:77% align:left position:16% size:64%
Your daddy always say,
"You listen to a horse,

00:07:26.680 --> 00:07:28.400 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
"he will tell you how he feels."

00:07:28.480 --> 00:07:30.480 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
OK, thanks, Barney.

00:07:32.160 --> 00:07:33.600 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
OK, come on.

00:07:34.640 --> 00:07:37.600 line:77% align:middle position:50% size:80%
TRACK ANNOUNCER: We are calling for
trainer Gary Mandela.

00:07:37.680 --> 00:07:40.800 line:77% align:middle position:50% size:80%
Gary Mandela,
please contact the jockey room.

00:07:40.880 --> 00:07:42.800 line:77% align:right size:80% position:90%
MR CRANE: Well, I tell you,
I don't know.

00:07:42.880 --> 00:07:46.600 line:77% align:left position:20% size:60%
The leg feels fine but she keeps...
she keeps jumping at that.

00:07:46.680 --> 00:07:48.280 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
She wants to get back in her stall.

00:07:48.360 --> 00:07:50.640 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
Vamos, Sonya. Vamos.

00:07:50.720 --> 00:07:52.880 line:83% align:middle position:50% size:80%
(Speaks Spanish) Sonya!

00:07:52.960 --> 00:07:54.840 line:77% align:left position:18% size:62%
She never does this ever.
<c.black>..............</c>She gonna race today?

00:07:54.920 --> 00:07:58.560 line:77% align:left position:18% size:62%
Of course she's gonna race today.
<c.black>.......</c>Hello, Mr Palmer.

00:08:00.200 --> 00:08:03.040 line:77% align:left position:16% size:64%
<c.black>..................</c>Nice to see you.
Wasn't sure you were coming today.

00:08:04.200 --> 00:08:06.120 line:77% align:left position:28% size:52%
I, er...I don't believe
<c.black>.......</c>I've ever met...

00:08:06.200 --> 00:08:08.240 line:83% align:middle position:50% size:80%
Prince Tariq Abal.

00:08:09.760 --> 00:08:13.840 line:77% align:left position:16% size:64%
Well, well. Sonya is just as pretty
as she is fast.

00:08:14.880 --> 00:08:17.600 line:77% align:right size:80% position:90%
Sir, I'll met you at our box
after I talk to my staff.

00:08:19.080 --> 00:08:20.480 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
Alright, what's the story here?

00:08:20.560 --> 00:08:22.160 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
Well, she's acting funny.

00:08:22.240 --> 00:08:25.400 line:77% align:left position:16% size:64%
Some heat in that right front
this morning.

00:08:25.480 --> 00:08:27.720 line:83% align:left position:16% size:64%
I'm not sure she wants to run today.

00:08:27.800 --> 00:08:30.360 line:77% align:right size:80% position:90%
I don't feel any heat in that leg.
What did the vet say?

00:08:30.440 --> 00:08:32.600 line:77% align:left position:16% size:64%
The vet and the paddock judge
took a look at her.

00:08:32.680 --> 00:08:34.080 line:83% align:left position:16% size:64%
They passed her as fine, but...

00:08:34.160 --> 00:08:35.680 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
Well, good. That's all that matters.

00:08:35.760 --> 00:08:38.800 line:77% align:left position:16% size:64%
Sir, I'm just saying I don't...
I don't think she should go today.

00:08:38.880 --> 00:08:43.640 line:77% align:right size:80% position:90%
Prince Tariq flew his personal 737
8,000 miles for what?

00:08:44.680 --> 00:08:47.720 line:77% align:left position:16% size:64%
I dunno - to win
the Jansen Handicap, I guess.

00:08:47.800 --> 00:08:49.560 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
To beat his brother Sadir.

00:08:49.640 --> 00:08:52.360 line:77% align:right size:80% position:90%
Tariq only flies in
when he can see one of his horses

00:08:52.440 --> 00:08:54.360 line:77% align:right size:80% position:90%
run against one of
his brother's horses.

00:08:54.440 --> 00:08:56.760 line:77% align:left position:16% size:64%
Mr Palmer, we're messing with
a champion two-year-old here,

00:08:56.840 --> 00:08:58.520 line:77% align:left position:16% size:64%
who's won her first two races
this year.

00:08:58.600 --> 00:09:02.000 line:77% align:right size:80% position:90%
Well, this'll make three. She's
a little star. No doubt about it.

00:09:02.080 --> 00:09:03.640 line:77% align:left position:16% size:64%
She's a lot more than a star,
Everett.

00:09:04.720 --> 00:09:06.280 line:77% align:left position:16% size:64%
Look, I'm just
listening to the horse.

00:09:06.360 --> 00:09:08.520 line:77% align:left position:16% size:64%
She's telling me
she could do better with some rest.

00:09:08.600 --> 00:09:12.080 line:77% align:right size:80% position:90%
Well, you'd do better by listening
to me. Look, she's a nice horse.

00:09:12.160 --> 00:09:13.680 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
But I've spent millions of dollars

00:09:13.760 --> 00:09:15.520 line:77% align:right size:80% position:90%
developing a stable of horses
for Prince Tariq

00:09:15.600 --> 00:09:17.120 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
so he can beat his brother.

00:09:17.200 --> 00:09:18.840 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
Now, I know you got big plans.

00:09:18.920 --> 00:09:22.960 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
But just do your job. OK?

00:09:23.040 --> 00:09:26.400 line:77% align:right size:80% position:90%
Daily maintenance,
overseeing the workouts - your job.

00:09:26.480 --> 00:09:29.000 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
Picking her races - my job.

00:09:30.040 --> 00:09:31.480 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
Are we good?

00:09:32.520 --> 00:09:33.960 line:77% align:left position:18% size:62%
Yeah, we're good.
<c.black>..............................</c>Good.

00:09:34.040 --> 00:09:35.640 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
She's morning-line favourite.

00:09:37.040 --> 00:09:38.480 line:77% align:left position:24% size:56%
<c.black>.......................</c>Let's go.
(Whinnies)

00:09:38.560 --> 00:09:40.800 line:77% align:right size:80% position:90%
Have one of the Mexicans
walk her around to settle her.

00:09:48.200 --> 00:09:49.640 line:83% align:middle position:50% size:80%
OK.

00:09:50.840 --> 00:09:52.480 line:83% align:middle position:50% size:80%
You heard the boss. Let's go.

00:09:52.560 --> 00:09:55.520 line:83% align:middle position:50% size:80%
( FANFARE PLAYS )

00:09:59.760 --> 00:10:01.760 line:77% align:middle position:50% size:80%
RACE CALLER: The field
for this afternoon's eighth race,

00:10:01.840 --> 00:10:04.200 line:77% align:middle position:50% size:80%
the Jensen Handicap,
now coming onto the track.

00:10:04.280 --> 00:10:08.080 line:77% align:middle position:50% size:80%
Number 2, Ocean's Blend,
carrying two pounds overweight.

00:10:08.160 --> 00:10:09.840 line:77% align:left position:32% size:48%
<c.black>.....</c>Number 8...
Do you own a horse, sweetie?

00:10:11.080 --> 00:10:12.720 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
This is just for owners.

00:10:12.760 --> 00:10:14.120 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
MR CRANE: Cale.

00:10:15.160 --> 00:10:16.600 line:83% align:left position:26% size:54%
Cale.

00:10:19.720 --> 00:10:21.200 line:83% align:left position:66% size:14%
(Chuckles)

00:10:21.240 --> 00:10:23.240 line:77% align:left position:18% size:62%
Hey, hey! Yeow!
<c.black>.............</c>Hey!

00:10:23.320 --> 00:10:25.120 line:77% align:left position:16% size:64%
<c.black>.......................</c>I'll be back.
Yes, sir.

00:10:26.200 --> 00:10:28.880 line:77% align:left position:16% size:64%
See her, honey? Look at that.
Number 5. Right there.

00:10:28.960 --> 00:10:30.880 line:77% align:left position:18% size:62%
That's our girl.
<c.black>.........</c>Think she'll win?

00:10:30.960 --> 00:10:34.200 line:77% align:middle position:50% size:80%
I got £10 that says she's gonna win.
(Laughs)

00:10:36.880 --> 00:10:38.920 line:83% align:middle position:50% size:80%
(Horse whinnies)

00:10:43.080 --> 00:10:46.600 line:83% align:middle position:50% size:80%
(Horse whinnies)

00:10:49.320 --> 00:10:50.800 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
Here we go, baby.

00:10:56.480 --> 00:10:58.480 line:83% align:middle position:50% size:80%
( STARTING BELL RINGS )

00:11:03.840 --> 00:11:05.640 line:83% align:middle position:50% size:80%
Easy. Nice and easy, now.

00:11:18.240 --> 00:11:20.480 line:77% align:left position:38% size:42%
MANOLIN: Yeah, yeah, yes!
Come on, sweetheart! Yeah!

00:11:20.560 --> 00:11:22.000 line:83% align:middle position:50% size:80%
Go, Sonya!

00:11:26.840 --> 00:11:30.240 line:77% align:left position:16% size:64%
Well, maybe this is your day.
Come on.

00:11:38.840 --> 00:11:40.280 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
Bring it home, baby.

00:11:41.840 --> 00:11:43.240 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
Come on, Sonya.

00:11:49.160 --> 00:11:50.840 line:83% align:middle position:50% size:80%
(Horse shrieks)

00:11:50.920 --> 00:11:52.840 line:83% align:middle position:50% size:80%
( CROWD GASPS )

00:12:08.040 --> 00:12:10.600 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
(Whinnies weakly)

00:12:13.440 --> 00:12:14.880 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
(Mutters)

00:12:29.800 --> 00:12:31.440 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
It's OK. I got it here.

00:12:31.520 --> 00:12:32.920 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
It's the cannon bone.

00:12:33.000 --> 00:12:34.760 line:77% align:right size:80% position:90%
Look, I'm sorry, Ben.
We gotta put her down.

00:12:34.840 --> 00:12:37.640 line:77% align:middle position:50% size:80%
Is she alright?
Doc. Balon. Manny. Whoa!

00:12:37.720 --> 00:12:39.880 line:83% align:middle position:50% size:80%
Easy, girl, easy. Come on. It's OK.

00:12:39.960 --> 00:12:43.760 line:77% align:left position:18% size:62%
Not here. Not here. Take her
back to her stall, but not here.

00:12:43.840 --> 00:12:45.960 line:77% align:left position:18% size:62%
Come on.
<c.black>..........................</c>Attagirl.

00:12:46.040 --> 00:12:48.360 line:83% align:middle position:50% size:80%
(Sonya whinnies in distress)

00:12:52.080 --> 00:12:54.080 line:83% align:middle position:50% size:80%
( RAIN FALLS )

00:12:54.160 --> 00:12:56.160 line:77% align:left position:16% size:64%
Ben, I can't put her down
until you sign this.

00:12:56.240 --> 00:12:58.000 line:77% align:left position:30% size:50%
No, Dan. I want to get
<c.black>....</c>some X-rays taken.

00:12:58.080 --> 00:13:00.040 line:77% align:left position:26% size:54%
Cale, come here. Come on.
Stay out of the way.

00:13:00.120 --> 00:13:02.200 line:77% align:left position:16% size:64%
What's the point, Ben?
She's finished.

00:13:02.280 --> 00:13:03.840 line:77% align:left position:18% size:62%
(Sonya whinnies)
<c.black>.............</c>I do not believe this.

00:13:03.920 --> 00:13:07.640 line:77% align:left position:18% size:62%
I told him!
<c.black>..</c>What? What did you tell me?

00:13:07.720 --> 00:13:10.040 line:77% align:left position:22% size:58%
I warned you she wasn't right.
<c.black>.......</c>You put the saddle on her.

00:13:10.120 --> 00:13:12.200 line:77% align:left position:18% size:62%
What?! Wait a minute.
<c.black>...........</c>Ben, look, I understand.

00:13:12.280 --> 00:13:14.240 line:77% align:right size:80% position:90%
It's sad when these things happen
in the racing business.

00:13:14.320 --> 00:13:16.520 line:77% align:left position:22% size:58%
Sad?!
<c.black>....</c>Yes, sad. This is an athlete.

00:13:16.600 --> 00:13:20.040 line:77% align:left position:16% size:64%
Well, then you just knowingly
killed a £750,000 athlete.

00:13:20.120 --> 00:13:21.880 line:77% align:left position:18% size:62%
We need to make a move.
<c.black>...................</c>PALMER: Tell me.

00:13:21.960 --> 00:13:23.400 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
It's her cannon bone, Mr Palmer.

00:13:23.480 --> 00:13:25.920 line:77% align:left position:18% size:62%
You pushed her.
She'd have run in the Breeders' Cup.

00:13:26.000 --> 00:13:27.400 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
She was special!

00:13:27.480 --> 00:13:30.320 line:77% align:left position:16% size:64%
And now she's got a broken leg
and it's over, so let it go.

00:13:33.600 --> 00:13:38.000 line:77% align:right size:80% position:90%
You don't care about anybody,
do you? Horses or people.

00:13:38.080 --> 00:13:39.680 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
Well, in fact, I do, Ben,

00:13:39.760 --> 00:13:42.520 line:77% align:left position:16% size:64%
and that's why I'm giving you
the opportunity to find a new job.

00:13:42.600 --> 00:13:43.920 line:77% align:left position:16% size:64%
<c.black>..................</c>Are you firing me?
That's right.

00:13:43.960 --> 00:13:45.560 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
You can take your Mexicans with you.

00:13:49.880 --> 00:13:52.760 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
They're men, Palmer. They got names.

00:13:52.840 --> 00:13:54.400 line:83% align:middle position:50% size:80%
(Sonya whinnies)

00:13:54.480 --> 00:13:56.040 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
You owe me money.

00:13:56.120 --> 00:13:58.720 line:77% align:left position:20% size:60%
You'll get your cheque first of
the month, like everybody else.

00:13:58.760 --> 00:14:01.040 line:77% align:left position:16% size:64%
No, you pay me now.
£9,000 for the last three months.

00:14:03.360 --> 00:14:05.360 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
Here's £6,000. £6,000.

00:14:05.440 --> 00:14:07.840 line:77% align:left position:16% size:64%
<c.black>...............</c>Take it or leave it.
I'll leave it. We agreed on £9,000.

00:14:07.920 --> 00:14:09.440 line:77% align:left position:18% size:62%
You're £3,000 short.
<c.black>.............</c>You wait for a cheque.

00:14:09.520 --> 00:14:11.040 line:77% align:left position:18% size:62%
I'm not waiting for a cheque!
<c.black>.......</c>(Sonya whinnies)

00:14:11.080 --> 00:14:12.920 line:77% align:left position:36% size:44%
For God's sake,
PLEASE put that horse down!

00:14:13.000 --> 00:14:14.880 line:77% align:left position:18% size:62%
Dan, Dan, Dan, wait!
<c.black>...........</c>(Snorts)

00:14:18.000 --> 00:14:20.120 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
I'll take the £6,000 and the horse.

00:14:21.560 --> 00:14:24.720 line:77% align:left position:16% size:64%
£6,000 and a dead horse and
I never have to hear from you again?

00:14:24.800 --> 00:14:26.560 line:77% align:left position:16% size:64%
<c.black>.......................</c>That's right.
Take the money.

00:14:26.640 --> 00:14:28.160 line:83% align:middle position:50% size:80%
(Sonya whinnies)

00:14:28.240 --> 00:14:31.160 line:77% align:left position:16% size:64%
Sedate her, Dan.
Put her down heavy for the night.

00:14:31.240 --> 00:14:33.800 line:77% align:left position:16% size:64%
It'll cost you £400
just to dispose of her body.

00:14:33.840 --> 00:14:35.280 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
Balon, hook up a trailer, would you?

00:14:35.320 --> 00:14:37.320 line:77% align:left position:16% size:64%
You got a hard head, Ben,
just like your old man.

00:14:37.400 --> 00:14:40.400 line:77% align:left position:16% size:64%
<c.black>.......</c>Cale, go on out to the truck.
On a horse farm with no horses.

00:14:40.480 --> 00:14:42.800 line:77% align:right size:80% position:90%
Go on. Manny,
take her out to the truck.

00:14:42.880 --> 00:14:45.240 line:77% align:left position:16% size:64%
Delusional. It's like a disease
with you Cranes.

00:14:45.320 --> 00:14:47.760 line:77% align:left position:16% size:64%
Better get out of here
before it rubs off on her.

00:14:49.960 --> 00:14:52.320 line:83% align:middle position:50% size:80%
(Sonya whinnies in distress)

00:14:52.400 --> 00:14:55.360 line:83% align:middle position:50% size:80%
( RAIN FALLS )

00:14:59.760 --> 00:15:01.520 line:77% align:left position:18% size:62%
BEN: Manny!
<c.black>...........................</c>Yeah?

00:15:01.600 --> 00:15:03.240 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
Go get the old man.

00:15:03.320 --> 00:15:05.240 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
Tell him it's an emergency.

00:15:14.520 --> 00:15:16.720 line:77% align:left position:16% size:64%
Alright, Balon, we need
the heavy winch and the sling

00:15:16.800 --> 00:15:18.200 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
to get her in this stall.

00:15:18.280 --> 00:15:20.840 line:77% align:left position:16% size:64%
<c.black>............</c>BALON: OK, where's that?
It's in the back stall there.

00:15:20.920 --> 00:15:22.520 line:83% align:middle position:50% size:80%
BALON: Oh, OK. I got it.

00:15:22.600 --> 00:15:25.400 line:77% align:right size:80% position:90%
Where have you been?
God, I've been so worried.

00:15:26.440 --> 00:15:28.560 line:77% align:left position:16% size:64%
<c.black>....................</c>What's going on?
I had a horse go down.

00:15:28.640 --> 00:15:30.480 line:77% align:left position:16% size:64%
<c.black>.........................</c>Oh, my God.
OK, anything else, boss?

00:15:30.560 --> 00:15:32.560 line:77% align:right size:80% position:90%
Yeah, give Balon a hand back there,
will you?

00:15:32.640 --> 00:15:34.760 line:77% align:left position:42% size:38%
<c.black>..............</c>Manny.
Balon.

00:15:34.840 --> 00:15:37.080 line:77% align:right size:80% position:90%
MAN: What would you geniuses
be calling an 'emergency'

00:15:37.160 --> 00:15:38.720 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
at night in the rain?

00:15:41.920 --> 00:15:43.800 line:83% align:middle position:50% size:80%
This about a horse?

00:15:47.120 --> 00:15:48.560 line:83% align:middle position:50% size:80%
Goodnight.

00:15:53.680 --> 00:15:56.200 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
I never ask you for anything.

00:15:56.280 --> 00:15:58.960 line:77% align:left position:16% size:64%
That's right.
I haven't heard from you in months.

00:15:59.040 --> 00:16:00.880 line:77% align:left position:16% size:64%
That's why your business
is so great.

00:16:00.960 --> 00:16:04.120 line:77% align:right size:80% position:90%
I got a filly in there
with a broken cannon bone, Pop.

00:16:05.440 --> 00:16:06.880 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
Thoroughbred?

00:16:08.360 --> 00:16:09.800 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
Racer?

00:16:15.680 --> 00:16:16.880 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
Put her down.

00:16:20.840 --> 00:16:23.720 line:77% align:right size:80% position:90%
You had a horse with
a shattered cannon bone once.

00:16:23.800 --> 00:16:25.800 line:77% align:right size:80% position:90%
You harnessed it up somehow
so it couldn't move.

00:16:25.840 --> 00:16:27.400 line:77% align:right size:80% position:90%
The leg healed
and that horse was fine.

00:16:27.480 --> 00:16:29.680 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
That was a long time ago.

00:16:29.760 --> 00:16:31.480 line:77% align:left position:16% size:64%
You were just a little boy,
Benjamin.

00:16:32.520 --> 00:16:35.240 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
But I remember it. It worked.

00:16:36.680 --> 00:16:39.560 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
He was an old lead pony.

00:16:39.640 --> 00:16:42.600 line:77% align:left position:16% size:64%
Healed just enough to walk around
for a few more years

00:16:42.680 --> 00:16:45.520 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
before I finally put him down.

00:16:45.600 --> 00:16:48.160 line:77% align:left position:16% size:64%
Which is what you'd do
if you had any sense at all.

00:16:58.080 --> 00:16:59.680 line:83% align:middle position:50% size:80%
Let's get her in the stall.

00:17:01.360 --> 00:17:04.560 line:77% align:left position:16% size:64%
<c.black>...............................</c>Cale.
He wanted me to help them, Mom.

00:17:04.640 --> 00:17:06.600 line:77% align:left position:16% size:64%
Cale, I'm gonna
spend the night with her.

00:17:06.680 --> 00:17:08.360 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
You go on inside with Mom, now.

00:17:09.840 --> 00:17:11.480 line:77% align:left position:22% size:58%
Alright.
<c.black>......</c>Right up there?

00:17:11.560 --> 00:17:13.280 line:77% align:left position:18% size:62%
Yep. Alright.
<c.black>.........</c>Right, Manny?

00:17:13.360 --> 00:17:16.080 line:77% align:left position:18% size:62%
You got the big winch?
<c.black>.......</c>Yeah, yeah, yeah.

00:17:17.320 --> 00:17:19.520 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
Let's hook it up. Come on.

00:17:41.960 --> 00:17:43.400 line:83% align:left position:30% size:50%
(Exhales)

00:17:46.120 --> 00:17:48.480 line:77% align:left position:16% size:64%
<c.black>............</c>DOC: Was it a hard fall?
Well, hard enough.

00:17:48.560 --> 00:17:51.640 line:77% align:left position:16% size:64%
She didn't get bumped or anything.
She...she just went down.

00:17:51.720 --> 00:17:53.680 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
That's the one from the track

00:17:53.760 --> 00:17:55.520 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
and my X-rays confirm it.

00:17:55.600 --> 00:17:58.000 line:77% align:right size:80% position:90%
It's a spiral fracture
of the cannon bone.

00:17:58.040 --> 00:18:00.720 line:77% align:left position:18% size:62%
But it is non-displaced.
<c.black>...</c>She'll never race again?

00:18:01.760 --> 00:18:04.520 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
No, honey. But she might walk again.

00:18:04.600 --> 00:18:07.840 line:77% align:right size:80% position:90%
There's a chance. It's up to her.
Try and keep her calm.

00:18:07.920 --> 00:18:11.560 line:77% align:right size:80% position:90%
Stable rest.
That cast I put on her should hold.

00:18:11.640 --> 00:18:13.520 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
I'll go real easy on her, Doc.

00:18:13.600 --> 00:18:15.200 line:77% align:left position:32% size:48%
<c.black>.........</c>Stay close on this.
BEN: You got it.

00:18:15.280 --> 00:18:18.400 line:77% align:left position:16% size:64%
Alright, let's pull
all the harness stuff.

00:18:18.480 --> 00:18:20.760 line:77% align:left position:16% size:64%
Put the straps, the pulley
in the tack room.

00:18:20.840 --> 00:18:24.760 line:77% align:right size:80% position:90%
Ben, when Mr Palmer fired you and us
yesterday, well...

00:18:24.840 --> 00:18:26.880 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
Well, we all don't have no jobs.

00:18:26.960 --> 00:18:30.000 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
I'm sorry, guys. I forgot. Here.

00:18:30.080 --> 00:18:31.720 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
Here's £1,000 each.

00:18:35.040 --> 00:18:36.480 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
What's wrong?

00:18:37.520 --> 00:18:39.680 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
Well, we train racehorses, right?

00:18:39.760 --> 00:18:42.240 line:77% align:right size:80% position:90%
And she's not gonna
race no more so...

00:18:42.320 --> 00:18:43.760 line:83% align:middle position:50% size:80%
So why are we gonna hang around

00:18:43.840 --> 00:18:45.720 line:77% align:left position:24% size:56%
<c.black>...........</c>and help you get
a broken racehorse to walk?

00:18:46.960 --> 00:18:48.800 line:83% align:left position:16% size:64%
You know who this horse was sired by?

00:18:50.040 --> 00:18:53.240 line:83% align:left position:16% size:64%
Dreamcatcher. You know who that was?

00:18:56.200 --> 00:18:58.000 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
Pop, who was Dreamcatcher?

00:18:59.480 --> 00:19:02.160 line:83% align:middle position:50% size:80%
Won the Dubai World Cup in '96.

00:19:02.240 --> 00:19:06.320 line:77% align:middle position:50% size:80%
Won seven of eleven Graded Stakes
and over £3 million.

00:19:06.400 --> 00:19:10.120 line:77% align:right size:80% position:90%
We get her healed enough
to breed her to a decent stud,

00:19:10.200 --> 00:19:12.920 line:77% align:right size:80% position:90%
sell that yearling for,
I dunno, maybe...

00:19:13.000 --> 00:19:17.480 line:77% align:left position:16% size:64%
If it's a colt with good
confirmation, maybe £300,000.

00:19:17.560 --> 00:19:19.400 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
BEN: £300,000.

00:19:19.480 --> 00:19:22.560 line:77% align:left position:28% size:52%
You two be interested
in a piece of £300,000?

00:19:24.240 --> 00:19:26.360 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
(Both laugh) Yeah!

00:19:27.560 --> 00:19:29.000 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
How about it, Pop?

00:19:32.240 --> 00:19:35.040 line:77% align:right size:80% position:90%
BALON: Looks good to me.
Another one done.

00:19:36.080 --> 00:19:38.360 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
BEN: Come on, take it up.

00:19:38.440 --> 00:19:40.600 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
Got it.

00:19:40.680 --> 00:19:42.600 line:83% align:middle position:50% size:80%
(Groans and whinnies)

00:19:44.120 --> 00:19:47.560 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
Good girl. Good Sonya.

00:19:51.200 --> 00:19:52.600 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
(Whinnies)

00:19:52.680 --> 00:19:55.320 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
Easy. Easy, girl. Easy, girl.

00:19:55.400 --> 00:19:56.840 line:83% align:left position:68% size:12%
Come on.

00:20:02.520 --> 00:20:05.440 line:77% align:left position:34% size:46%
(Sonya whinnies)
<c.black>...........</c>One, two, three.

00:20:05.520 --> 00:20:07.000 line:83% align:middle position:50% size:80%
(Whinnies)

00:20:08.560 --> 00:20:10.600 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
(Children call goodbye)

00:20:16.280 --> 00:20:18.120 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
One, two, three.

00:20:22.200 --> 00:20:23.880 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
OK, that's good. That's good. OK.

00:20:23.960 --> 00:20:25.440 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
BALON: She's OK.

00:20:28.080 --> 00:20:29.800 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
She's OK.

00:21:01.840 --> 00:21:03.840 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
(Sonya nickers quietly)

00:21:12.720 --> 00:21:14.280 line:83% align:middle position:50% size:80%
(Gasps)

00:21:14.440 --> 00:21:17.080 line:83% align:middle position:50% size:80%
(Whinnies and snorts)

00:21:18.480 --> 00:21:20.400 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
Whoa, whoa, whoa! Are you alright?

00:21:20.480 --> 00:21:21.920 line:77% align:left position:34% size:46%
I'm fine.
<c.black>...............</c>Huh? You OK?

00:21:22.000 --> 00:21:24.680 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
BALON: Sonya, take it easy. Come on.

00:21:24.760 --> 00:21:26.240 line:77% align:left position:18% size:62%
It's OK, honey.
<c.black>..........</c>How is she?

00:21:26.320 --> 00:21:28.680 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
She's OK.

00:21:28.760 --> 00:21:31.680 line:77% align:right size:80% position:90%
What were you doing?!
She...she's not a pet, Cale.

00:21:31.760 --> 00:21:33.360 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
She's what I do for work now,

00:21:33.440 --> 00:21:35.520 line:77% align:right size:80% position:90%
so you're gonna have to
leave her be, alright?

00:21:37.960 --> 00:21:40.000 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
Sorry.

00:21:41.520 --> 00:21:44.000 line:77% align:left position:18% size:62%
Are you sure you're alright?
<c.black>..........................</c>Fine.

00:21:54.440 --> 00:21:56.080 line:83% align:middle position:50% size:80%
(Snorts quietly)

00:22:01.440 --> 00:22:03.440 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
( DOOR OPENS )

00:22:55.240 --> 00:22:56.680 line:83% align:middle position:50% size:80%
(Snuffles)

00:22:59.600 --> 00:23:01.360 line:83% align:middle position:50% size:80%
(Sniffs)

00:23:02.600 --> 00:23:04.120 line:83% align:middle position:50% size:80%
(Nickers quietly)

00:23:08.520 --> 00:23:11.360 line:83% align:middle position:50% size:80%
(Snorts and snuffles)

00:23:15.560 --> 00:23:18.320 line:83% align:middle position:50% size:80%
(Munches)

00:23:36.320 --> 00:23:37.760 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
(Sonya munches)

00:23:44.400 --> 00:23:45.880 line:83% align:middle position:50% size:80%
(Snuffles)

00:23:46.920 --> 00:23:48.360 line:83% align:middle position:50% size:80%
(Nickers)

00:23:53.600 --> 00:23:56.960 line:77% align:left position:42% size:38%
(Whinnies)
<c.black>....</c>(Footsteps retreat)

00:23:57.040 --> 00:23:59.320 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
(Whinnies quietly)

00:24:13.000 --> 00:24:15.760 line:83% align:middle position:50% size:80%
( DOOR CREAKS )

00:24:21.120 --> 00:24:23.160 line:77% align:left position:16% size:64%
<c.black>........................</c>Here you go.
Thank you.

00:24:26.720 --> 00:24:29.440 line:77% align:left position:16% size:64%
Make all that money and get to
eat as much pie as you want?

00:24:29.520 --> 00:24:31.480 line:77% align:right size:80% position:90%
(Chuckles)
Yeah, you can't find a better job.

00:24:31.560 --> 00:24:33.480 line:77% align:left position:20% size:60%
<c.black>.........................</c>(Laughs)
(Laughs)

00:24:34.520 --> 00:24:36.680 line:77% align:left position:16% size:64%
Manny's gonna take me
to watch him ride a racehorse

00:24:36.760 --> 00:24:39.200 line:77% align:left position:16% size:64%
and then tonight I'm gonna
muck out Sonya's stall.

00:24:39.280 --> 00:24:41.040 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
Thinking about painting it.

00:24:41.120 --> 00:24:42.560 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
Nice to have a horse, huh?

00:24:43.720 --> 00:24:45.840 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
Especially after Dad said,

00:24:45.920 --> 00:24:49.160 line:77% align:left position:16% size:64%
"There will never be another horse
on this farm as long as I live."

00:24:51.040 --> 00:24:52.480 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
Did Pop tell you that?

00:24:54.360 --> 00:24:56.560 line:77% align:right size:80% position:90%
Don't you listen to
everything Pop says.

00:24:56.640 --> 00:24:58.640 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
There's two sides to every story.

00:24:58.720 --> 00:25:02.320 line:77% align:left position:16% size:64%
Pop said Dad's the best horseman.
Says he has a gift.

00:25:03.360 --> 00:25:04.840 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
Well, that's true.

00:25:06.040 --> 00:25:07.480 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
We all know that's true.

00:25:20.800 --> 00:25:22.960 line:77% align:left position:48% size:32%
Hey.
Hello.

00:25:23.040 --> 00:25:25.800 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
Whoa, Zephyr. Whoa, boy.

00:25:25.880 --> 00:25:27.760 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
Thanks, Mike.

00:25:29.080 --> 00:25:31.600 line:77% align:left position:16% size:64%
<c.black>......</c>What did you think about that?
That was fast.

00:25:31.680 --> 00:25:34.880 line:77% align:left position:18% size:62%
Nice boots.
<c.black>.....................</c>Ah, thank you.

00:25:34.960 --> 00:25:37.520 line:77% align:right size:80% position:90%
Just saddled a couple of horses
for a few owners.

00:25:43.560 --> 00:25:45.280 line:83% align:middle position:50% size:80%
(Sighs)

00:25:45.360 --> 00:25:47.080 line:77% align:left position:46% size:34%
<c.black>....</c>Pretty cool, huh?
Yeah.

00:25:52.440 --> 00:25:54.600 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
You ever ride in races?

00:25:56.200 --> 00:25:58.120 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
Couple of times I did.

00:25:58.200 --> 00:25:59.760 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
But no more.

00:25:59.840 --> 00:26:01.280 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
Why?

00:26:01.360 --> 00:26:03.520 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
Ah...

00:26:03.600 --> 00:26:06.520 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
..I have bad dreams.

00:26:12.800 --> 00:26:15.880 line:77% align:left position:16% size:64%
Three years ago
I got my first real race.

00:26:15.960 --> 00:26:17.840 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
I ran fifth.

00:26:19.080 --> 00:26:21.040 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
What was the name of the horse?

00:26:22.680 --> 00:26:25.240 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
Downtown Swing.

00:26:26.520 --> 00:26:27.920 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
He was amazing.

00:26:28.040 --> 00:26:29.760 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
Did you ever ride him again?

00:26:29.840 --> 00:26:32.760 line:77% align:left position:16% size:64%
Yeah. In his second race
I was flying into that first turn.

00:26:33.800 --> 00:26:36.840 line:77% align:left position:16% size:64%
Then I looked under my arm
to see if I was clear on the rail.

00:26:36.880 --> 00:26:40.120 line:77% align:left position:16% size:64%
When I looked back up,
there was a horse swerving into me.

00:26:40.200 --> 00:26:43.520 line:77% align:left position:16% size:64%
My left foot came outta the iron,
I fell to the ground

00:26:43.600 --> 00:26:46.200 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
and I got run over by three horses.

00:26:47.440 --> 00:26:49.560 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
Broke both shoulders,

00:26:49.640 --> 00:26:51.360 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
sternum,

00:26:51.440 --> 00:26:53.000 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
four ribs,

00:26:53.080 --> 00:26:54.520 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
a punctured lung.

00:26:56.080 --> 00:26:57.760 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
You never raced again?

00:26:59.360 --> 00:27:01.520 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
(Sighs) 

00:27:01.600 --> 00:27:04.920 line:77% align:left position:16% size:64%
You know,
at night when I fall asleep...

00:27:06.560 --> 00:27:09.400 line:77% align:left position:16% size:64%
..I dream I'm in a big race
on a very fast horse.

00:27:10.720 --> 00:27:14.560 line:77% align:left position:16% size:64%
I look to my left foot, it slips out
of the iron and I begin to fall.

00:27:14.640 --> 00:27:17.840 line:77% align:left position:16% size:64%
But before I hit the ground,
I wake up.

00:27:19.040 --> 00:27:21.840 line:77% align:left position:16% size:64%
<c.black>..</c>But you still exercise racehorses.
Yeah.

00:27:21.960 --> 00:27:24.880 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
It's just...

00:27:24.960 --> 00:27:26.800 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
..it's just me and the horse,

00:27:26.880 --> 00:27:30.600 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
alone on the track, free,

00:27:30.680 --> 00:27:32.680 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
no-one to bother us.

00:27:32.760 --> 00:27:34.640 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
It's much better that way.

00:27:35.880 --> 00:27:37.560 line:77% align:right size:80% position:90%
I'm sorry about your nightmares,
Manny.

00:27:37.640 --> 00:27:39.080 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
It's OK.

00:27:40.320 --> 00:27:42.880 line:77% align:left position:16% size:64%
It's God's way of telling me
no more racing.

00:28:01.040 --> 00:28:03.360 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
(Sonya whinnies)

00:28:08.320 --> 00:28:10.840 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
(Munches)

00:28:12.000 --> 00:28:13.600 line:83% align:middle position:50% size:80%
'Night.

00:28:19.400 --> 00:28:21.000 line:83% align:middle position:50% size:80%
(Sonya whinnies)

00:28:30.560 --> 00:28:32.080 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
From Mom.

00:28:32.160 --> 00:28:34.080 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
I'm good. Just put it down.

00:28:45.440 --> 00:28:46.880 line:83% align:middle position:50% size:80%
Cale.

00:28:48.600 --> 00:28:51.040 line:77% align:left position:16% size:64%
Can you grab that roll of wire
underneath the fence there?

00:28:51.120 --> 00:28:52.640 line:83% align:middle position:50% size:80%
Yeah.

00:28:58.720 --> 00:29:01.080 line:77% align:left position:16% size:64%
<c.black>............</c>Just hang onto it there.
OK.

00:29:06.120 --> 00:29:07.880 line:77% align:left position:16% size:64%
Pop said
this farm used to be beautiful.

00:29:09.640 --> 00:29:11.480 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
This farm WAS beautiful.

00:29:12.880 --> 00:29:17.680 line:77% align:right size:80% position:90%
200 acres.
One of the nicest in Versailles.

00:29:17.760 --> 00:29:19.960 line:77% align:left position:16% size:64%
<c.black>............</c>See all that over there?
Yeah.

00:29:21.480 --> 00:29:22.920 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
Well, that was ours.

00:29:28.880 --> 00:29:32.040 line:77% align:right size:80% position:90%
Pop's owned
some really nice race mares.

00:29:33.720 --> 00:29:36.640 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
Big, beautiful female horses.

00:29:36.680 --> 00:29:40.240 line:77% align:left position:16% size:64%
Wave Land, Blue Jezebel
and Miss Muffet.

00:29:40.320 --> 00:29:42.000 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
That's right.

00:29:44.640 --> 00:29:47.920 line:77% align:left position:16% size:64%
Pop said he built those stalls
and filled them with horses.

00:29:48.000 --> 00:29:51.360 line:77% align:right size:80% position:90%
Yeah, he made a good living
selling yearlings.

00:29:51.440 --> 00:29:54.040 line:77% align:left position:16% size:64%
But you wanted to keep yearlings
and race them, right?

00:29:57.200 --> 00:29:59.560 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
Well, it got kinda hard.

00:29:59.640 --> 00:30:02.000 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
We had some horses born on this farm

00:30:02.080 --> 00:30:03.920 line:77% align:right size:80% position:90%
go on to win big races
for somebody else.

00:30:04.000 --> 00:30:05.960 line:77% align:left position:16% size:64%
So you got Pop
to keep some of the yearlings

00:30:06.040 --> 00:30:07.520 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
so you could train 'em, race 'em?

00:30:07.600 --> 00:30:10.760 line:77% align:right size:80% position:90%
You don't just keep 'em, Cale.
They're not free.

00:30:10.840 --> 00:30:13.280 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
I'm gonna brush down Sonya.

00:30:25.760 --> 00:30:27.240 line:83% align:left position:30% size:50%
Cale Crane?

00:30:27.280 --> 00:30:28.720 line:83% align:middle position:50% size:80%
Yes, ma'am.

00:30:28.800 --> 00:30:30.560 line:77% align:right size:80% position:90%
Are you working on
your creative writing assignment?

00:30:30.640 --> 00:30:32.120 line:83% align:middle position:50% size:80%
Yes, ma'am.

00:30:32.160 --> 00:30:34.280 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
What's your story about?

00:30:36.120 --> 00:30:37.880 line:83% align:middle position:50% size:80%
It's about a king

00:30:37.960 --> 00:30:40.560 line:83% align:middle position:50% size:80%
in his castle.

00:30:41.960 --> 00:30:43.840 line:83% align:middle position:50% size:80%
And a magic horse.

00:30:45.440 --> 00:30:47.960 line:83% align:middle position:50% size:80%
( GENTLE MUSIC )

00:31:13.560 --> 00:31:15.040 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
'Bye!

00:31:30.160 --> 00:31:32.000 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
She can stand on it.

00:31:32.080 --> 00:31:35.400 line:77% align:left position:16% size:64%
Not for long...
but she can stand on it.

00:31:38.760 --> 00:31:41.200 line:77% align:left position:16% size:64%
I'll run a couple more tests
in the morning, Ben,

00:31:41.280 --> 00:31:43.600 line:77% align:left position:16% size:64%
but I don't see any reason
she can't breed - she looks good.

00:31:43.680 --> 00:31:47.280 line:77% align:left position:16% size:64%
You helped her, Cale.
She's gonna have a baby! Yeah!

00:31:47.360 --> 00:31:48.880 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
I'll see you Friday.

00:31:51.680 --> 00:31:53.920 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
Well, I'm gonna call in a favour.

00:31:57.440 --> 00:31:59.320 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
(Whispers) Go, Cale.

00:31:59.400 --> 00:32:01.200 line:77% align:left position:18% size:62%
(Makes horse noises)
<c.black>...............................</c>Go!

00:32:10.200 --> 00:32:11.880 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
So where are you going?

00:32:11.960 --> 00:32:14.400 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
Gonna go see an old friend.

00:32:19.720 --> 00:32:21.280 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
About a stud for Sonya?

00:32:21.320 --> 00:32:24.320 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
Yeah, about a stud.

00:32:40.760 --> 00:32:42.200 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
You wanna come?

00:32:43.240 --> 00:32:45.600 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
Yeah, I'll come.

00:33:13.560 --> 00:33:17.360 line:77% align:left position:16% size:64%
Fusaichi Pegasus,
who won the Kentucky Derby.

00:33:17.440 --> 00:33:18.840 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
Did you see him?

00:33:18.920 --> 00:33:20.360 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
It's Fusaichi.

00:33:21.640 --> 00:33:23.400 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
Giant's Causeway.

00:33:27.480 --> 00:33:30.240 line:77% align:right size:80% position:90%
Johannesburg,
who won the Breeders' Cup Juvenile.

00:33:31.840 --> 00:33:34.200 line:83% align:middle position:50% size:80%
Did you learn all that from Pop too?

00:33:34.280 --> 00:33:36.560 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
He's a beautiful horse.

00:33:36.640 --> 00:33:39.600 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
Hey, Bill, it's good to see you.

00:33:39.720 --> 00:33:41.120 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
Good to see you.

00:33:41.200 --> 00:33:42.760 line:77% align:left position:36% size:44%
This is my daughter, Cale.
<c.black>..................</c>Hi.

00:33:42.840 --> 00:33:45.320 line:77% align:left position:18% size:62%
Nice to meet you, Cale.
<c.black>..............</c>Nice to meet you too.

00:33:45.400 --> 00:33:47.240 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
So, Ben, you call me two months ago

00:33:47.320 --> 00:33:49.560 line:77% align:left position:16% size:64%
telling me you've got this race mare
needs to be covered,

00:33:49.640 --> 00:33:51.640 line:77% align:left position:16% size:64%
you need a favour,
then I don't hear from you.

00:33:51.720 --> 00:33:53.880 line:77% align:right size:80% position:90%
Well, it's been a pretty long road
with that filly, Bill,

00:33:53.960 --> 00:33:55.560 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
but she's ready to go now.

00:33:55.600 --> 00:33:58.160 line:77% align:right size:80% position:90%
So, are you still gonna be able
to help me out here?

00:33:59.360 --> 00:34:00.840 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
Right over here.

00:34:02.440 --> 00:34:04.000 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
Alright, ladies and gentlemen,

00:34:04.080 --> 00:34:06.640 line:77% align:right size:80% position:90%
are you ready
for the world's greatest stud?

00:34:06.720 --> 00:34:09.320 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
Come on, Todd, bring him on out.

00:34:12.920 --> 00:34:14.520 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
That's not...

00:34:15.720 --> 00:34:18.240 line:77% align:left position:18% size:62%
What is that?
<c.black>..........</c>This here's Thunderpants.

00:34:18.280 --> 00:34:22.040 line:77% align:left position:16% size:64%
Honey,
Thunderpants is a teaser pony.

00:34:22.120 --> 00:34:26.000 line:77% align:left position:16% size:64%
He's gonna help Sonya get ready
to go into the breeding shed

00:34:26.080 --> 00:34:27.600 line:83% align:left position:16% size:64%
with the stallion.

00:34:27.680 --> 00:34:29.280 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
Thank you, Bill.

00:34:29.360 --> 00:34:31.440 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
Hey, Cale,

00:34:31.520 --> 00:34:33.600 line:77% align:right size:80% position:90%
want to meet the stallion
I picked for ya?

00:34:33.640 --> 00:34:36.440 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
( HORSE WHINNIES )

00:34:36.520 --> 00:34:39.400 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
Cale, meet Grand Slam.

00:34:41.040 --> 00:34:42.520 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
Grand Slam?

00:34:44.520 --> 00:34:46.160 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
Unbelievable.

00:34:52.440 --> 00:34:54.920 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
So...what do you think?

00:34:56.280 --> 00:34:57.760 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
(Exhales)

00:34:57.840 --> 00:34:59.880 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
Well, I think it's Grand Slam.

00:34:59.960 --> 00:35:01.640 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
(Chuckles)

00:35:01.720 --> 00:35:04.400 line:77% align:left position:16% size:64%
Everyone at Ashford
has a lot of respect for your family.

00:35:04.480 --> 00:35:05.960 line:83% align:left position:16% size:64%
I explained your situation

00:35:06.040 --> 00:35:08.200 line:77% align:left position:16% size:64%
and they want to do you
the favour of a lifetime.

00:35:08.280 --> 00:35:09.800 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
I just...I don't know what to say.

00:35:09.840 --> 00:35:11.760 line:77% align:left position:16% size:64%
Say you'll have your filly here
first week in May.

00:35:11.840 --> 00:35:13.240 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
You got it.

00:35:13.320 --> 00:35:14.920 line:77% align:left position:16% size:64%
That week's the only shot you get.
<c.black>.................................</c>OK.

00:35:15.000 --> 00:35:16.400 line:83% align:left position:16% size:64%
He's booked till next year.

00:35:16.480 --> 00:35:20.040 line:77% align:left position:16% size:64%
And you've gotta send me half of
the £15,000 by the end of the week.

00:35:21.360 --> 00:35:24.080 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
That's, ah...£15,000. Ah...

00:35:24.160 --> 00:35:28.600 line:77% align:left position:16% size:64%
Well, Grand Slam's normal stud fees
are £200,000.

00:35:28.680 --> 00:35:30.480 line:77% align:left position:16% size:64%
We're waiving that completely.
<c.black>................</c>Yeah, I know, but...

00:35:30.560 --> 00:35:32.840 line:77% align:left position:16% size:64%
The £15,000 doesn't even cover
our costs and insurance.

00:35:32.920 --> 00:35:35.680 line:77% align:right size:80% position:90%
No, Bill, it's an amazing offer.
I just didn't, you know, I-I...

00:35:35.760 --> 00:35:38.800 line:77% align:right size:80% position:90%
I'm wondering, though,
if maybe I couldn't, you know,

00:35:38.880 --> 00:35:42.160 line:77% align:right size:80% position:90%
give you a share in the foal
to cover all the expenses,

00:35:42.200 --> 00:35:43.560 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
whatever they are.

00:35:43.640 --> 00:35:46.320 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
We...we just don't do that.

00:35:46.400 --> 00:35:47.960 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
Not in a case like this.

00:35:49.360 --> 00:35:51.120 line:77% align:left position:16% size:64%
Are you saying
you want to call it off?

00:35:51.200 --> 00:35:52.880 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
No, it's...

00:35:54.200 --> 00:35:56.000 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
Bill, I don't have the money.

00:35:57.400 --> 00:36:01.800 line:77% align:left position:16% size:64%
I'm sorry, Ben.
I didn't fully know your situation.

00:36:01.880 --> 00:36:05.280 line:77% align:right size:80% position:90%
That's OK, Bill. Listen,
I really appreciate you trying.

00:36:05.360 --> 00:36:08.200 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
I'm gonna call, alright? Thanks.

00:36:08.280 --> 00:36:09.800 line:83% align:middle position:50% size:80%
Let's go, honey.

00:36:19.320 --> 00:36:21.680 line:77% align:right size:80% position:90%
POP: I've never seen
Grand Slam up close.

00:36:21.760 --> 00:36:23.680 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
CALE: He's got muscles everywhere.

00:36:23.760 --> 00:36:25.240 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
What did he say?

00:36:27.800 --> 00:36:29.280 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
He's a horse.

00:36:29.320 --> 00:36:31.160 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
I know. What did he say?

00:36:33.760 --> 00:36:36.080 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
"I am a great champion."

00:36:37.640 --> 00:36:39.680 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
"When I ran, the ground shook,

00:36:39.760 --> 00:36:42.400 line:77% align:left position:16% size:64%
"the sky opened
and mere mortals parted..."

00:36:42.440 --> 00:36:44.280 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
"..the way to victory.

00:36:44.360 --> 00:36:47.080 line:77% align:right size:80% position:90%
"And I met my owner
in the winner's circle."

00:36:47.120 --> 00:36:49.320 line:77% align:left position:16% size:64%
"Where he put a blanket of flowers
on my back."

00:36:49.400 --> 00:36:51.160 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
(Laughs) You remembered that.

00:36:52.360 --> 00:36:54.800 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
Sport of kings, you know that?

00:36:54.880 --> 00:36:57.280 line:77% align:right size:80% position:90%
They call horseracing
the sport of kings.

00:36:58.360 --> 00:37:00.600 line:77% align:left position:16% size:64%
So when are you going to take me
to the races?

00:37:00.640 --> 00:37:04.080 line:77% align:right size:80% position:90%
I don't go anymore.
Haven't been in years.

00:37:08.160 --> 00:37:11.040 line:77% align:left position:16% size:64%
So I can take the racing form
and 'The Blood-Horse', right?

00:37:11.120 --> 00:37:13.760 line:77% align:right size:80% position:90%
Your dad doesn't want
me teaching you about horses.

00:37:13.800 --> 00:37:16.560 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
So I should leave 'em?

00:37:16.600 --> 00:37:18.680 line:77% align:right size:80% position:90%
You should stuff 'em
under your shirt.

00:37:18.720 --> 00:37:20.440 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
(Laughs) OK.

00:37:23.960 --> 00:37:25.640 line:77% align:right size:80% position:90%
Cale, in that cabinet
above the sink...

00:37:26.680 --> 00:37:28.320 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
Yeah.

00:37:28.400 --> 00:37:30.000 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
..is there a coffee can?

00:37:30.080 --> 00:37:31.480 line:83% align:middle position:50% size:80%
Mm-hm.

00:37:31.560 --> 00:37:33.960 line:77% align:left position:16% size:64%
<c.black>.....</c>Bring it to your dad, would ya?
Sure.

00:37:34.040 --> 00:37:35.600 line:83% align:middle position:50% size:80%
Goodnight.

00:37:35.680 --> 00:37:37.120 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
Goodnight.

00:37:47.360 --> 00:37:50.680 line:77% align:left position:16% size:64%
<c.black>..</c>Pop wanted me to give this to you.
Thanks, hon.

00:37:50.760 --> 00:37:53.600 line:77% align:left position:16% size:64%
I'm gonna eat my dessert in the barn.
<c.black>.....</c>Alright.

00:38:06.600 --> 00:38:08.280 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
(Sighs)

00:38:12.480 --> 00:38:14.200 line:77% align:left position:16% size:64%
<c.black>.........</c>BEN: What the hell is this?
POP: Coffee can.

00:38:14.280 --> 00:38:16.480 line:77% align:left position:16% size:64%
<c.black>............</c>You expect me to use it?
It's the only flavour I got.

00:38:16.520 --> 00:38:19.920 line:77% align:right size:80% position:90%
You're unbelievable.
There's almost £20,000 there.

00:38:22.120 --> 00:38:24.520 line:77% align:right size:80% position:90%
You watched me
sell this farm off bit by bit

00:38:24.600 --> 00:38:26.400 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
till there was nothing left.

00:38:26.480 --> 00:38:30.280 line:77% align:left position:16% size:64%
<c.black>.............</c>Why are you doing this?
Damned if I know.

00:38:32.160 --> 00:38:33.600 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
Breed the horse, Ben.

00:38:35.160 --> 00:38:36.560 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
Picking up that filly

00:38:36.640 --> 00:38:38.560 line:77% align:left position:16% size:64%
was the gutsiest thing
I've seen you do in years.

00:38:38.640 --> 00:38:40.040 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
Don't talk to me about guts.

00:38:40.120 --> 00:38:42.280 line:77% align:right size:80% position:90%
I took the biggest swing I could
and I struck out.

00:38:42.360 --> 00:38:44.160 line:77% align:left position:18% size:62%
Then you gave up.
<c.black>......................</c>I broke, Pop!

00:38:44.240 --> 00:38:46.200 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
What do you expect me to do?

00:38:46.280 --> 00:38:47.960 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
I expect you to take the money,

00:38:48.000 --> 00:38:50.800 line:77% align:left position:16% size:64%
trust your instincts,
and breed the horse.

00:38:50.880 --> 00:38:52.320 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
You told me to put her down.

00:38:52.400 --> 00:38:54.080 line:77% align:left position:16% size:64%
But you didn't, did you?
'Cause you're a horseman.

00:38:54.120 --> 00:38:55.640 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
Oh, don't blow smoke...

00:38:55.680 --> 00:38:58.360 line:77% align:left position:16% size:64%
Are you gonna spend your life
shovelling horse squat for sheiks

00:38:58.440 --> 00:39:00.440 line:77% align:left position:16% size:64%
or are you gonna
get back in the game?

00:39:06.080 --> 00:39:08.920 line:77% align:right size:80% position:90%
Don't think I don't know what's
going on here with you and Cale.

00:39:09.000 --> 00:39:11.120 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
It's in her blood, Ben.

00:39:11.200 --> 00:39:12.960 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
Cale's a beautiful kid.

00:39:13.040 --> 00:39:14.640 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
And I don't want this life for her,

00:39:14.720 --> 00:39:16.400 line:77% align:right size:80% position:90%
so stop filling her head
with horse stories.

00:39:16.480 --> 00:39:18.960 line:77% align:left position:18% size:62%
Horse stories are all I got.
<c.black>...</c>Good, then keep 'em to yourself.

00:39:19.040 --> 00:39:20.800 line:77% align:right size:80% position:90%
I'll pay you back
when the foal sells.

00:39:20.840 --> 00:39:22.960 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
(Slams door)

00:39:33.920 --> 00:39:35.760 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
Any chance you'll keep the foal?

00:39:37.000 --> 00:39:38.560 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
Race him or her?

00:39:38.640 --> 00:39:40.520 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
No, we're gonna sell the foal.

00:39:40.600 --> 00:39:43.000 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
But we'll still have Sonador.

00:39:43.080 --> 00:39:44.760 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
Sonador?

00:39:44.840 --> 00:39:47.200 line:83% align:left position:16% size:64%
Yeah, that's her full name - Sonador.

00:39:50.720 --> 00:39:52.200 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
Sonador.

00:39:52.280 --> 00:39:54.080 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
It's Spanish.

00:39:54.160 --> 00:39:56.480 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
Spanish for 'dreamer'.

00:39:59.000 --> 00:40:00.720 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
Goodnight, Dreamer.

00:40:02.280 --> 00:40:04.840 line:77% align:left position:16% size:64%
<c.black>.......................</c>OK, I got it.
I'm going to Pop's.

00:40:12.360 --> 00:40:16.160 line:77% align:left position:16% size:64%
Lil, how many days did they give you
down at the diner?

00:40:17.400 --> 00:40:19.720 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
I got Monday, Wednesday and Friday

00:40:19.800 --> 00:40:22.080 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
but I could take more.

00:40:22.160 --> 00:40:24.560 line:77% align:left position:16% size:64%
Palmer called around -
pretty much shut me out everywhere.

00:40:24.600 --> 00:40:26.280 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
I can't find any work.

00:40:29.600 --> 00:40:31.640 line:83% align:left position:16% size:64%
I'm gonna have to take down the sign.

00:40:32.480 --> 00:40:34.120 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
The real estate sign?

00:40:34.200 --> 00:40:36.000 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
It's all been sold.

00:40:36.080 --> 00:40:38.800 line:77% align:left position:16% size:64%
Only land we got left to sell
we're sitting on.

00:40:38.840 --> 00:40:41.040 line:77% align:left position:16% size:64%
Here's the first letter
of foreclosure.

00:40:47.040 --> 00:40:48.880 line:77% align:left position:18% size:62%
Morning.
<c.black>..........</c>DOC FLEMING: Hello, Cale.

00:40:49.000 --> 00:40:51.480 line:77% align:left position:18% size:62%
BALON: Hey, Doc.
<c.black>......................</c>Balon. Manny.

00:40:51.760 --> 00:40:52.960 line:77% align:left position:24% size:56%
Sonya's gonna make us some money,
huh?

00:40:53.120 --> 00:40:55.000 line:77% align:left position:20% size:60%
This horse,
she gonna make a special baby, huh?

00:40:55.080 --> 00:40:57.400 line:77% align:left position:16% size:64%
<c.black>..................</c>Is Ben around?
Yeah, right here.

00:40:57.480 --> 00:40:59.720 line:77% align:middle position:50% size:80%
Alright, I just got off the phone
with Bill.

00:40:59.800 --> 00:41:02.320 line:77% align:left position:16% size:64%
<c.black>...........</c>We're back on.
BALON: Oh, yes!

00:41:02.400 --> 00:41:03.880 line:83% align:middle position:50% size:80%
Gonna breed her to Grand Slam.

00:41:03.960 --> 00:41:07.600 line:77% align:right size:80% position:90%
Ben, I've completed my tests
and I've got some bad news for you.

00:41:08.840 --> 00:41:10.520 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
What?

00:41:10.600 --> 00:41:12.320 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
She's infertile.

00:41:15.920 --> 00:41:17.800 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
She's not gonna have a baby now?

00:41:17.880 --> 00:41:20.040 line:77% align:right size:80% position:90%
No, honey,
she's never gonna have babies.

00:41:25.400 --> 00:41:27.720 line:83% align:middle position:50% size:80%
I'm sorry, guys.

00:41:34.520 --> 00:41:35.920 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
(Quietly) Sorry, Sonya.

00:41:36.000 --> 00:41:37.720 line:83% align:left position:48% size:32%
It's OK.

00:41:56.000 --> 00:41:57.440 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
It's almost dawn.

00:41:58.480 --> 00:42:00.920 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
You've been up all night.

00:42:01.000 --> 00:42:04.880 line:77% align:right size:80% position:90%
What was I thinking, Lil,
trying to breed that horse?

00:42:06.720 --> 00:42:08.240 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
Cale loves that horse.

00:42:08.360 --> 00:42:10.760 line:77% align:right size:80% position:90%
That's good 'cause that little filly
just ruined us.

00:42:11.880 --> 00:42:15.480 line:77% align:left position:16% size:64%
That little filly is the best thing
that's ever happened around here.

00:42:15.560 --> 00:42:17.280 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
Oh, come on, Lil.

00:42:17.360 --> 00:42:20.200 line:77% align:left position:16% size:64%
Since she's been in that barn,
we have a family

00:42:20.280 --> 00:42:22.600 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
for the first time in years.

00:42:22.680 --> 00:42:25.640 line:77% align:left position:16% size:64%
Look, I'll work seven days a week
at the diner

00:42:25.720 --> 00:42:27.840 line:77% align:left position:16% size:64%
if it means you'll spend time
with your daughter.

00:42:27.880 --> 00:42:30.800 line:77% align:left position:16% size:64%
Can't you see
how much she wants to be with you?

00:42:33.520 --> 00:42:37.720 line:77% align:left position:16% size:64%
And I know
that your dad disappointed you

00:42:37.760 --> 00:42:40.960 line:77% align:left position:16% size:64%
but that does not mean
that you have to disappoint her.

00:42:41.040 --> 00:42:42.760 line:77% align:right size:80% position:90%
This has nothing
to do with my father.

00:42:42.800 --> 00:42:44.280 line:77% align:left position:16% size:64%
It has everything
to do with your father.

00:42:44.320 --> 00:42:45.880 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
You're wrong!

00:42:45.960 --> 00:42:48.120 line:77% align:left position:16% size:64%
Truth is, if Cale
hadn't have been with me that night,

00:42:48.200 --> 00:42:49.800 line:77% align:left position:16% size:64%
I'd have left that horse
on the track

00:42:49.880 --> 00:42:52.920 line:77% align:left position:16% size:64%
or let them put the horse down.
Then I'd still have my job.

00:42:54.160 --> 00:42:56.240 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
Cale, I...

00:43:06.320 --> 00:43:07.880 line:83% align:middle position:50% size:80%
Cale.

00:43:08.080 --> 00:43:09.480 line:83% align:middle position:50% size:80%
(Knocks on door)

00:43:09.560 --> 00:43:11.400 line:83% align:middle position:50% size:80%
Come on, Cale.

00:43:12.720 --> 00:43:14.440 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
Honey, can I come in?

00:43:14.520 --> 00:43:17.240 line:77% align:left position:16% size:64%
Come on.
Let's just give her some time.

00:43:17.360 --> 00:43:21.000 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
Cale? Come on, honey, open the door.

00:43:21.080 --> 00:43:23.000 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
(Knocks) Please.

00:43:23.120 --> 00:43:24.880 line:77% align:left position:16% size:64%
She'll come downstairs
when she's ready.

00:43:39.440 --> 00:43:40.920 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
We're gonna run away.

00:43:43.120 --> 00:43:45.560 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
(Sniffs) We're gonna run far away.

00:44:02.400 --> 00:44:04.040 line:83% align:left position:60% size:20%
There you go.

00:44:05.760 --> 00:44:07.560 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
Just gonna go for a little walk.

00:44:11.080 --> 00:44:12.360 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
Cale.

00:44:12.480 --> 00:44:13.920 line:77% align:left position:36% size:44%
<c.black>...........</c>( DOOR SLAMS )
(Whinnies)

00:44:16.360 --> 00:44:18.040 line:83% align:middle position:50% size:80%
Stop, Sonya!

00:44:18.120 --> 00:44:19.640 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
Sonya, stop!

00:44:27.000 --> 00:44:29.000 line:83% align:middle position:50% size:80%
( DRAMATIC MUSIC )

00:44:40.080 --> 00:44:41.560 line:83% align:middle position:50% size:80%
Hang on, Cale.

00:44:48.920 --> 00:44:49.920 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
Cale!

00:44:51.120 --> 00:44:52.520 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
Dad, she won't stop!

00:44:52.600 --> 00:44:54.040 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
I can't make her stop!

00:44:58.040 --> 00:44:59.960 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
Cale, hang on.

00:45:03.120 --> 00:45:04.440 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
Easy.

00:45:10.480 --> 00:45:12.440 line:83% align:middle position:50% size:80%
Cale, Cale!

00:45:12.520 --> 00:45:14.800 line:83% align:middle position:50% size:80%
Jump! Jump!

00:45:19.720 --> 00:45:22.680 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
I gotcha. I gotcha. I gotcha.

00:45:22.760 --> 00:45:25.920 line:77% align:left position:18% size:62%
Are you alright? Are you OK?
<c.black>..........................</c>Yes.

00:45:30.840 --> 00:45:32.600 line:77% align:left position:16% size:64%
<c.black>..........................</c>Is she OK?
It's alright. I've got her.

00:45:38.360 --> 00:45:40.200 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
Oh!

00:45:40.280 --> 00:45:42.960 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
It's alright, baby. It's OK.

00:45:45.400 --> 00:45:47.360 line:77% align:left position:18% size:62%
Are you OK, honey? 
<c.black>....................</c>(Shakily) Ye...

00:45:47.440 --> 00:45:48.880 line:77% align:left position:18% size:62%
Huh?
<c.black>..................</c>Yes.

00:45:53.720 --> 00:45:55.640 line:83% align:left position:32% size:48%
Hey, Ben?

00:45:57.520 --> 00:45:58.920 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
Ben, how's Cale doing?

00:45:59.000 --> 00:46:00.400 line:77% align:left position:32% size:48%
She's alright.
<c.black>.............</c>She OK?

00:46:00.480 --> 00:46:02.640 line:77% align:left position:28% size:52%
Yeah, she's...she's fine.
<c.black>.......................</c>Oh, OK.

00:46:02.720 --> 00:46:04.640 line:77% align:right size:80% position:90%
Can we talk to you
for a minute, boss?

00:46:04.720 --> 00:46:06.200 line:83% align:middle position:50% size:80%
Right. How's Sonya?

00:46:06.280 --> 00:46:10.200 line:77% align:left position:16% size:64%
She was running back and forth
along the fence and, ah...

00:46:10.280 --> 00:46:12.280 line:77% align:left position:16% size:64%
..we were following her
in the truck...

00:46:12.360 --> 00:46:14.240 line:77% align:right size:80% position:90%
Balon, did she break down?
How bad is she?

00:46:14.320 --> 00:46:16.400 line:77% align:right size:80% position:90%
Well, in the truck
it said that she's about,

00:46:16.480 --> 00:46:18.200 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
I don't know, a quarter-mile.

00:46:18.280 --> 00:46:19.800 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
Well, she, um...

00:46:19.880 --> 00:46:22.800 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
She was gettin' faster and faster.

00:46:22.960 --> 00:46:24.800 line:77% align:right size:80% position:90%
Yeah,
she's looking pretty strong, sir.

00:46:27.200 --> 00:46:29.280 line:83% align:middle position:50% size:80%
What are you...?

00:46:29.360 --> 00:46:31.000 line:83% align:middle position:50% size:80%
Are you saying she should race?

00:46:44.320 --> 00:46:46.160 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
You can load her up, John.

00:46:47.480 --> 00:46:50.560 line:77% align:middle position:50% size:80%
Mariah's Storm broke her leg
the same way as Sonya.

00:46:50.640 --> 00:46:52.440 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
Same fracture, same location.

00:46:52.520 --> 00:46:53.920 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
Who's Mariah's Storm?

00:46:54.000 --> 00:46:56.040 line:77% align:left position:24% size:56%
She was a great racehorse.
<c.black>...................</c>She sure was.

00:46:56.120 --> 00:46:57.520 line:83% align:middle position:50% size:80%
Made a big comeback too.

00:46:57.600 --> 00:46:59.560 line:77% align:right size:80% position:90%
Came back and beat Serena's Song
in the Graded Stakes.

00:46:59.680 --> 00:47:01.120 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
When I saw Sonya's X-rays,

00:47:01.200 --> 00:47:03.120 line:77% align:right size:80% position:90%
I thought I ought to
show it to you, Ben.

00:47:03.240 --> 00:47:05.200 line:77% align:left position:18% size:62%
That bone is healed.
<c.black>.........</c>Oh, yeah, that leg's good.

00:47:05.280 --> 00:47:07.920 line:77% align:right size:80% position:90%
But getting her back into
racing shape, that's up to you.

00:47:08.000 --> 00:47:09.560 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
Good luck.

00:47:09.640 --> 00:47:11.240 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
Thanks a lot, Doc.

00:47:11.320 --> 00:47:13.080 line:77% align:left position:50% size:30%
<c.black>.........</c>Yep. 'Bye.
Goodbye.

00:47:43.280 --> 00:47:45.320 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
Well, she's not favouring that leg.

00:47:48.120 --> 00:47:49.560 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
How's she look?

00:47:49.640 --> 00:47:51.600 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
She looks big.

00:47:51.680 --> 00:47:54.360 line:77% align:left position:18% size:62%
Big as in strong?
<c.black>.................</c>No, big as in fat.

00:47:55.760 --> 00:47:57.480 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
That's mean.

00:47:57.560 --> 00:47:59.360 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
That's mean. You shouldn't say that.

00:47:59.480 --> 00:48:02.200 line:77% align:right size:80% position:90%
Well, she's been eating
too many popsicles.

00:48:02.320 --> 00:48:04.160 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
(Laughs) What?

00:48:04.280 --> 00:48:06.680 line:77% align:right size:80% position:90%
'What?' You didn't know
I knew about that, did you?

00:48:06.760 --> 00:48:08.240 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
(Chuckles)

00:48:15.760 --> 00:48:17.960 line:77% align:left position:46% size:34%
37:02.
<c.black>......</c>37:02.

00:48:18.000 --> 00:48:19.520 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
36.

00:48:40.280 --> 00:48:41.840 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
What do you think?

00:48:43.720 --> 00:48:46.280 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
Well, in five weeks,

00:48:46.360 --> 00:48:50.360 line:77% align:left position:16% size:64%
the best she's done
is three furlongs in 37 seconds.

00:48:52.600 --> 00:48:54.480 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
Not fast enough to win much, is it?

00:48:54.560 --> 00:48:56.720 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
Maybe a cheap claimer

00:48:56.800 --> 00:48:58.640 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
or Bluegrass Downs.

00:48:59.680 --> 00:49:01.720 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
She was a Graded Stakes horse.

00:49:01.800 --> 00:49:04.920 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
Now she's a claimer.

00:49:05.000 --> 00:49:08.240 line:77% align:right size:80% position:90%
Might be a good idea
to run her in one.

00:49:08.320 --> 00:49:11.640 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
See if she perks up in a real race.

00:49:11.720 --> 00:49:13.560 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
Yeah, I've been thinking about that.

00:49:14.880 --> 00:49:16.960 line:77% align:left position:16% size:64%
You don't think
anybody would claim her, do you?

00:49:18.480 --> 00:49:20.400 line:77% align:right size:80% position:90%
Would you buy a horse
that broke its leg?

00:49:22.760 --> 00:49:24.760 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
Well, she might win.

00:49:27.840 --> 00:49:30.160 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
Could be easy money.

00:49:30.240 --> 00:49:33.720 line:77% align:middle position:50% size:80%
RACE CALLER: And away they go.
Getting away to a beautiful start.

00:49:33.920 --> 00:49:36.320 line:77% align:middle position:50% size:80%
And Super 35
from the extreme outside.

00:49:36.360 --> 00:49:38.320 line:77% align:middle position:50% size:80%
Coming from behind into the race,
Sonador.

00:49:41.600 --> 00:49:44.080 line:77% align:left position:28% size:52%
Little lady looks pretty good.
<c.black>........</c>Yeah.

00:49:47.800 --> 00:49:50.040 line:77% align:left position:36% size:44%
Come on, Sonya.
<c.black>.........</c>Come on, Sonador.

00:49:50.120 --> 00:49:51.680 line:77% align:left position:26% size:54%
<c.black>................</c>Come on.
Can you see her?

00:49:51.800 --> 00:49:53.600 line:77% align:middle position:50% size:80%
And fourth into the straight,
Sonador.

00:49:53.680 --> 00:49:55.560 line:83% align:middle position:50% size:80%
And Sonador's on the far outside.

00:49:55.600 --> 00:49:58.160 line:77% align:middle position:50% size:80%
Then we have, back in fifth,
All for Nothing...

00:49:58.240 --> 00:50:00.040 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
Come on, baby.

00:50:00.120 --> 00:50:01.760 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
Come on, Mike, change her lead now.

00:50:01.880 --> 00:50:04.520 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
..coming around the far turn...

00:50:04.600 --> 00:50:06.360 line:77% align:left position:34% size:46%
<c.black>..............</c>Come on!
Come on, girl!

00:50:06.480 --> 00:50:08.560 line:77% align:middle position:50% size:80%
..comes Obvious Favorite,
Storm Boy's running in third...

00:50:08.680 --> 00:50:11.160 line:77% align:right size:80% position:90%
Come on, Sonya.
Only three furlongs to go now.

00:50:12.480 --> 00:50:13.480 line:83% align:middle position:50% size:80%
(Screams)

00:50:13.600 --> 00:50:15.800 line:77% align:middle position:50% size:80%
Major Easy and Obvious Favorite
are nose-to-nose...

00:50:15.880 --> 00:50:18.760 line:77% align:left position:48% size:32%
Show her the stick.
Get her out of there.

00:50:18.880 --> 00:50:21.240 line:83% align:middle position:50% size:80%
..in between horses...

00:50:27.720 --> 00:50:29.480 line:83% align:middle position:50% size:80%
(Horse whinnies)

00:50:32.480 --> 00:50:33.960 line:77% align:left position:34% size:46%
<c.black>....</c>(Squeals)
Third!

00:50:34.000 --> 00:50:35.320 line:77% align:left position:30% size:50%
Third.
<c.black>......</c>Third.

00:50:45.680 --> 00:50:48.720 line:77% align:right size:80% position:90%
01:13 - a little slow,
but it's the beginning.

00:50:48.800 --> 00:50:51.960 line:77% align:right size:80% position:90%
If Mike wouldn't have been boxed in,
I think she would've won, sir.

00:50:52.040 --> 00:50:53.680 line:83% align:middle position:50% size:80%
Whoo! (Laughs)

00:50:54.960 --> 00:50:57.200 line:77% align:left position:16% size:64%
It's third place.
So, what does she get?

00:50:57.280 --> 00:50:58.880 line:83% align:middle position:50% size:80%
£1,100.

00:50:58.960 --> 00:51:01.120 line:77% align:left position:18% size:62%
Sonador. Ben Crane?
<c.black>...................</c>Yeah.

00:51:01.200 --> 00:51:05.000 line:77% align:left position:18% size:62%
Claim.
<c.black>....</c>What?! You gotta be kidding me.

00:51:05.080 --> 00:51:07.520 line:77% align:left position:16% size:64%
<c.black>.............</c>Claim?
Wait a second. Hang on a minute.

00:51:07.600 --> 00:51:09.160 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
You said she wouldn't get claimed.

00:51:09.240 --> 00:51:10.840 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
Cale, listen to me.

00:51:10.920 --> 00:51:14.120 line:77% align:right size:80% position:90%
What was the tag?
How much did you get for her?

00:51:15.480 --> 00:51:16.920 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
£15,000.

00:51:19.280 --> 00:51:20.960 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
You just sold Sonador.

00:51:25.320 --> 00:51:26.800 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
I don't believe this.

00:51:51.480 --> 00:51:52.920 line:83% align:left position:28% size:52%
Cale...

00:51:54.480 --> 00:51:56.440 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
..I wasn't trying to sell Sonya.

00:51:58.840 --> 00:52:02.080 line:77% align:left position:16% size:64%
Out of a hundred horses that
could have been claimed tonight,

00:52:02.160 --> 00:52:03.560 line:83% align:left position:16% size:64%
you know how many got claimed?

00:52:03.640 --> 00:52:05.080 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
Two.

00:52:06.480 --> 00:52:09.200 line:77% align:left position:16% size:64%
Do you understand
that you've got to claim the horse

00:52:09.280 --> 00:52:10.840 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
before the race is even run?

00:52:10.920 --> 00:52:14.480 line:77% align:left position:16% size:64%
I just figured there's no way anybody
would take a chance on a filly

00:52:14.560 --> 00:52:16.120 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
that had already broken her leg.

00:52:16.160 --> 00:52:17.520 line:83% align:left position:62% size:18%
(Sighs)

00:52:17.600 --> 00:52:19.560 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
I guess there was some chance.

00:52:20.640 --> 00:52:22.080 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
She's gone.

00:52:30.040 --> 00:52:31.960 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
She was a good horse, Cale.

00:52:32.040 --> 00:52:33.560 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
I'm gonna miss her too.

00:52:33.640 --> 00:52:35.560 line:77% align:right size:80% position:90%
Please don't treat me
like a little kid.

00:52:35.680 --> 00:52:38.000 line:77% align:right size:80% position:90%
You should try to get
some of your money back.

00:52:38.120 --> 00:52:40.160 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
I get it. It's business.

00:52:41.720 --> 00:52:43.120 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
That's right. It is.

00:52:43.240 --> 00:52:44.840 line:83% align:left position:64% size:16%
(Sighs)

00:52:44.920 --> 00:52:46.880 line:77% align:left position:16% size:64%
But I wasn't trying
to sell Sonya, OK?

00:52:47.000 --> 00:52:48.400 line:83% align:left position:54% size:26%
You lied to me.

00:52:49.680 --> 00:52:52.600 line:77% align:left position:16% size:64%
You said I'd always have Sonador.
You stood right there and said it.

00:52:52.720 --> 00:52:54.360 line:83% align:middle position:50% size:80%
You raced her and she got claimed.

00:52:54.440 --> 00:52:56.360 line:77% align:right size:80% position:90%
Well, welcome to the world
of horseracing, Cale,

00:52:56.440 --> 00:52:58.600 line:77% align:right size:80% position:90%
where everything doesn't end up
the way you want it to.

00:52:58.680 --> 00:53:00.080 line:83% align:middle position:50% size:80%
She wasn't for sale!

00:53:00.120 --> 00:53:03.640 line:77% align:right size:80% position:90%
Every racehorse everywhere
in the world right now is for sale.

00:53:03.760 --> 00:53:05.120 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
Get that.

00:53:05.200 --> 00:53:07.480 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
She wasn't just some racehorse.

00:53:09.400 --> 00:53:11.000 line:83% align:left position:24% size:56%
She was our horse.

00:53:20.280 --> 00:53:23.240 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
( DOOR OPENS AND CLOSES )

00:53:33.680 --> 00:53:36.280 line:77% align:right size:80% position:90%
I told Pat that I was gonna
work the dinner shift tonight.

00:53:37.480 --> 00:53:38.880 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
Remember?

00:53:38.960 --> 00:53:41.120 line:77% align:right size:80% position:90%
You said you could go to
Cale's school for parents night.

00:53:41.200 --> 00:53:42.640 line:77% align:left position:18% size:62%
8:00. I'll be there.
<c.black>............................</c>Mm-hmm.

00:53:48.480 --> 00:53:49.920 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
Have a good time.

00:53:54.200 --> 00:53:55.920 line:83% align:middle position:50% size:80%
(Woman laughs) OK.

00:53:56.040 --> 00:53:59.320 line:77% align:middle position:50% size:80%
(Woman reads) "My shirt was wet
and it smelled like French toast

00:53:59.440 --> 00:54:01.120 line:83% align:middle position:50% size:80%
"so even though I threw up,

00:54:01.200 --> 00:54:03.560 line:77% align:middle position:50% size:80%
"I was happy my dad took me
to the firehouse.

00:54:03.680 --> 00:54:05.880 line:77% align:middle position:50% size:80%
"The end."
( LAUGHTER AND APPLAUSE )

00:54:05.960 --> 00:54:08.120 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
WOMAN: Thank you, Ms Richardson.

00:54:08.200 --> 00:54:09.760 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
Thank you.

00:54:11.680 --> 00:54:13.240 line:77% align:left position:32% size:48%
<c.black>..................</c>Ben Crane.
Yes, ma'am.

00:54:13.320 --> 00:54:14.840 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
I'd love you to read Cale's story.

00:54:14.960 --> 00:54:16.360 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
It's very inventive.

00:54:17.400 --> 00:54:19.960 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
It's right there in the blue folder.

00:54:20.040 --> 00:54:21.480 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
Come on up.

00:54:36.680 --> 00:54:38.080 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
(Reads) "Once upon a time,

00:54:38.160 --> 00:54:41.720 line:77% align:left position:16% size:64%
<c.black>....</c>"there was a noble king
who lived in a beautiful castle

00:54:41.800 --> 00:54:43.480 line:83% align:left position:22% size:58%
"overlooking green fields.

00:54:44.520 --> 00:54:47.000 line:77% align:middle position:50% size:80%
"An evil storm cast darkness
over his castle

00:54:47.080 --> 00:54:48.920 line:83% align:middle position:50% size:80%
"and before he knew it,

00:54:49.000 --> 00:54:51.560 line:77% align:middle position:50% size:80%
"dark knights had begun
to take away his kingdom

00:54:51.640 --> 00:54:53.320 line:83% align:middle position:50% size:80%
"one piece at a time.

00:54:53.400 --> 00:54:55.320 line:83% align:middle position:50% size:80%
"But our king was a warrior.

00:54:55.400 --> 00:54:58.720 line:77% align:middle position:50% size:80%
"And he knew that
if he could find his magic horse,

00:54:58.800 --> 00:55:01.360 line:77% align:middle position:50% size:80%
"he could restore the kingdom
to greatness.

00:55:01.440 --> 00:55:03.320 line:83% align:middle position:50% size:80%
"He was not like most kings.

00:55:03.400 --> 00:55:05.160 line:83% align:middle position:50% size:80%
"He was quiet and kind.

00:55:06.480 --> 00:55:09.080 line:77% align:middle position:50% size:80%
"Everyone loved the king,
which he may not have known.

00:55:10.680 --> 00:55:13.440 line:77% align:middle position:50% size:80%
"He searched and searched
and finally rescued his horse

00:55:13.520 --> 00:55:14.960 line:83% align:middle position:50% size:80%
"from a raging river.

00:55:17.240 --> 00:55:19.800 line:77% align:middle position:50% size:80%
"But by the time
he had freed his horse,

00:55:19.880 --> 00:55:23.160 line:77% align:middle position:50% size:80%
"his kingdom was gone
and he had given up.

00:55:25.120 --> 00:55:26.800 line:83% align:middle position:50% size:80%
"But the horse knew better than him.

00:55:29.120 --> 00:55:31.360 line:77% align:middle position:50% size:80%
"The horse took him
over mountain ranges

00:55:31.440 --> 00:55:34.000 line:83% align:middle position:50% size:80%
"and across...

00:55:34.080 --> 00:55:35.800 line:83% align:middle position:50% size:80%
"..raging rivers.

00:55:35.880 --> 00:55:38.000 line:77% align:middle position:50% size:80%
"When it finally looked like
they would die,

00:55:38.080 --> 00:55:40.360 line:83% align:middle position:50% size:80%
"the horse asked him to trust him.

00:55:41.880 --> 00:55:45.200 line:77% align:middle position:50% size:80%
"The king didn't know
if the horse had really spoken to him

00:55:45.280 --> 00:55:49.000 line:77% align:middle position:50% size:80%
"or he just hadn't had
anything to eat in a few days."

00:55:49.080 --> 00:55:50.800 line:83% align:middle position:50% size:80%
( QUIET LAUGHTER )

00:55:50.880 --> 00:55:54.880 line:77% align:middle position:50% size:80%
"Not soon after, the horse attempted
to climb a mountain so steep

00:55:54.960 --> 00:55:57.440 line:77% align:middle position:50% size:80%
"the king was sure
it would be their deaths.

00:55:59.120 --> 00:56:00.960 line:83% align:middle position:50% size:80%
"But the horse reached the top.

00:56:02.920 --> 00:56:05.680 line:77% align:left position:16% size:64%
<c.black>........</c>"And at the top,
they found his kingdom restored.

00:56:09.680 --> 00:56:12.600 line:83% align:middle position:50% size:80%
( TENDER MUSIC )

00:56:12.680 --> 00:56:16.640 line:77% align:middle position:50% size:80%
"All those who loved him
greeted the king with pie and coffee.

00:56:20.520 --> 00:56:21.960 line:83% align:middle position:50% size:80%
"By Cale Crane."

00:56:28.240 --> 00:56:29.680 line:77% align:left position:20% size:60%
Can we keep these?
<c.black>..............................</c>Yes.

00:56:55.680 --> 00:56:58.040 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
I read your story tonight at school.

00:57:01.400 --> 00:57:03.000 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
The stupid one about the king?

00:57:09.200 --> 00:57:10.640 line:83% align:left position:22% size:58%
Yeah. The stupid king.

00:57:12.800 --> 00:57:14.240 line:83% align:left position:36% size:44%
(Sighs)

00:57:17.080 --> 00:57:18.840 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
I make mistakes, Cale.

00:57:20.880 --> 00:57:22.320 line:83% align:left position:34% size:46%
I'm sorry.

00:57:28.000 --> 00:57:30.240 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
So you like the stupid king?

00:57:33.040 --> 00:57:34.840 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
Yeah. I like the stupid king.

00:57:38.000 --> 00:57:39.760 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
I love the stupid king.

00:57:41.760 --> 00:57:43.200 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
He loves you too.

00:58:04.080 --> 00:58:06.360 line:77% align:left position:16% size:64%
Ben, there's some guy here
to see ya.

00:58:09.240 --> 00:58:10.640 line:77% align:left position:22% size:58%
<c.black>..............</c>Cale.
Hmm?

00:58:10.720 --> 00:58:12.120 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
I got Pop a new goat.

00:58:12.200 --> 00:58:15.720 line:77% align:right size:80% position:90%
Do you want to go and pull him
out of the trailer? Thanks a lot.

00:58:25.440 --> 00:58:27.120 line:83% align:middle position:50% size:80%
(Whinnies)

00:58:28.160 --> 00:58:29.560 line:83% align:middle position:50% size:80%
Sonya!

00:58:29.640 --> 00:58:31.040 line:83% align:left position:66% size:14%
Sonya!

00:58:31.120 --> 00:58:32.560 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
You came home!

00:58:34.560 --> 00:58:36.000 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
I'm so glad you're back.

00:58:37.080 --> 00:58:38.480 line:83% align:middle position:50% size:80%
How did you get her back?

00:58:38.560 --> 00:58:40.520 line:77% align:left position:26% size:54%
Well, it wasn't just me.
Pop helped out too.

00:58:40.560 --> 00:58:42.480 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
(Sonya whinnies)

00:58:42.520 --> 00:58:43.680 line:83% align:left position:20% size:60%
I did?

00:58:44.760 --> 00:58:47.360 line:77% align:middle position:50% size:80%
Let's just say we're both
out of coffee for a while.

00:58:48.680 --> 00:58:51.400 line:77% align:middle position:50% size:80%
Alright.
I got all the paperwork here.

00:58:51.480 --> 00:58:54.880 line:77% align:left position:16% size:64%
Now, Cale,
I put 51% of Sonador in your name.

00:58:54.960 --> 00:58:58.880 line:77% align:left position:24% size:56%
So from here on out,
you make all the decisions.

00:58:58.920 --> 00:59:02.120 line:77% align:left position:16% size:64%
<c.black>.............</c>Don't worry -
I got you in there at 39%.

00:59:02.200 --> 00:59:04.200 line:77% align:left position:16% size:64%
Balon, you and Manny
can split the other 10%, huh?

00:59:04.280 --> 00:59:05.760 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
What are you saying, Ben?

00:59:05.800 --> 00:59:09.000 line:77% align:left position:16% size:64%
I'm saying as soon as
she signs this paper,

00:59:09.080 --> 00:59:12.680 line:77% align:left position:16% size:64%
the new owner of Sonador
is Cale Crane.

00:59:17.800 --> 00:59:20.920 line:77% align:left position:16% size:64%
Welcome to the race business.
Congratulations.

00:59:21.000 --> 00:59:22.560 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
You work for her now.

00:59:22.640 --> 00:59:24.320 line:83% align:middle position:50% size:80%
Oooh.

00:59:24.360 --> 00:59:26.680 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
BALON: OK, boss.

00:59:26.720 --> 00:59:28.600 line:77% align:left position:46% size:34%
CALE: OK.
<c.black>..</c>What's it gonna be?

00:59:28.680 --> 00:59:30.120 line:77% align:left position:36% size:44%
<c.black>............</c>CALE: Come on.
Let's go, senorita!

00:59:30.200 --> 00:59:31.640 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
Come on!

00:59:36.320 --> 00:59:38.040 line:83% align:left position:42% size:38%
(Yawns)

00:59:45.720 --> 00:59:47.240 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
Do you want me to warm her up?

00:59:47.320 --> 00:59:49.560 line:77% align:left position:16% size:64%
And then push her
for three furlongs? Or maybe four?

00:59:49.640 --> 00:59:51.560 line:77% align:left position:32% size:48%
You just want us
to blow her out today, right?

00:59:51.640 --> 00:59:53.560 line:77% align:left position:38% size:42%
Then we could start
to build her up, huh?

00:59:53.600 --> 00:59:56.600 line:83% align:left position:60% size:20%
Um...

00:59:56.680 --> 00:59:58.600 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
Yeah. Let's just blow her out.

01:00:21.520 --> 01:00:23.160 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
BEN: Appreciate it, Bob.

01:00:23.200 --> 01:00:24.760 line:77% align:right size:80% position:90%
If anything comes up,
you let me know, huh?

01:00:24.840 --> 01:00:26.440 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
Alright. Goodnight.

01:00:28.200 --> 01:00:29.600 line:83% align:left position:66% size:14%
Hey.

01:00:29.680 --> 01:00:31.160 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
You're up kinda late.

01:00:31.200 --> 01:00:33.120 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
I'm reading all of Sonya's records.

01:00:34.160 --> 01:00:36.320 line:77% align:left position:16% size:64%
She won over £200,000
in Graded company.

01:00:36.400 --> 01:00:38.040 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
Oh, yeah. I know.

01:00:38.120 --> 01:00:40.520 line:77% align:left position:16% size:64%
Qualifies her for
a lot of Stakes races.

01:00:40.640 --> 01:00:42.680 line:77% align:left position:16% size:64%
I was looking through
the conditions book.

01:00:45.520 --> 01:00:47.480 line:77% align:right size:80% position:90%
Well, I'm sure
you'll figure something out.

01:00:51.080 --> 01:00:53.640 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
I want you to help me.

01:00:53.760 --> 01:00:55.320 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
I want you to help me train her.

01:00:59.000 --> 01:01:00.440 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
I see.

01:01:01.480 --> 01:01:03.320 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
Well, you'd be getting a trainer.

01:01:03.440 --> 01:01:05.840 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
What is it I'd be getting?

01:01:06.880 --> 01:01:08.720 line:77% align:left position:24% size:56%
10%.
<c.black>.......................</c>20%.

