01:01:20.720 --> 01:01:22.160 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
That's it.

01:01:22.240 --> 01:01:23.640 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
There.

01:01:23.760 --> 01:01:25.640 line:83% align:middle position:50% size:80%
