(Taps glass loudly)

01:01:35.720 --> 01:01:37.280 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
BEN: Alright. Here we go.

01:01:37.360 --> 01:01:38.800 line:77% align:left position:28% size:52%
<c.black>................</c>Here we go.
BALON: Hello. Hello.

01:01:40.080 --> 01:01:41.840 line:83% align:middle position:50% size:80%
I want to thank everyone for coming.

01:01:41.920 --> 01:01:44.760 line:77% align:middle position:50% size:80%
And I have scouted
all of Sonador's possible races.

01:01:44.840 --> 01:01:46.600 line:77% align:middle position:50% size:80%
And I've picked one
I know she can win.

01:01:46.680 --> 01:01:48.080 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
LILLY: Really?

01:01:48.200 --> 01:01:49.560 line:77% align:left position:18% size:62%
MANOLIN: Very nice.
<c.black>.........................</c>POP: Good.

01:01:49.640 --> 01:01:51.040 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
LILLY: And when is this race?

01:01:51.120 --> 01:01:52.920 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
Saturday, October 29.

01:01:53.000 --> 01:01:55.240 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
I've gotten the best jockey.

01:01:55.320 --> 01:01:57.040 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
His name is Manolin Vallarta.

01:01:59.600 --> 01:02:02.160 line:77% align:left position:18% size:62%
Wait. I'm Manolin Vallarta.
<c.black>..................</c>LILLY: Good idea.

01:02:02.240 --> 01:02:04.800 line:77% align:left position:16% size:64%
You once told me you were
the greatest jockey in the world.

01:02:04.880 --> 01:02:06.680 line:77% align:left position:18% size:62%
And I believe you.
<c.black>...............</c>(Laughs)

01:02:06.760 --> 01:02:08.400 line:83% align:middle position:50% size:80%
Thank you, Cale.

01:02:08.640 --> 01:02:10.680 line:77% align:left position:30% size:50%
Thank you but I can't.
<c.black>........</c>I'm not ready.

01:02:10.800 --> 01:02:12.160 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
I'm, um...

01:02:12.240 --> 01:02:14.640 line:77% align:right size:80% position:90%
"Fat, and I've gotta slim down."
Right, Manny?

01:02:14.760 --> 01:02:17.280 line:83% align:middle position:50% size:80%
I'm sure 29 October is the same day

01:02:17.360 --> 01:02:19.640 line:77% align:middle position:50% size:80%
as the running of the
Breeders' Cup Championship, isn't it?

01:02:19.760 --> 01:02:21.480 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
Biggest day in racing.

01:02:21.560 --> 01:02:24.360 line:77% align:left position:22% size:58%
Yeah. The Breeders' Cup is, what,
eight races, worth £14 million?

01:02:24.480 --> 01:02:26.680 line:77% align:right size:80% position:90%
I don't think you want to run
in any race

01:02:26.760 --> 01:02:28.400 line:77% align:right size:80% position:90%
on the same day
as the Breeders' Cup.

01:02:28.520 --> 01:02:29.880 line:83% align:left position:30% size:50%
You're right.

01:02:29.960 --> 01:02:32.720 line:77% align:left position:16% size:64%
We shouldn't run in any race
the same day as Breeders' Cup.

01:02:35.040 --> 01:02:37.400 line:77% align:left position:16% size:64%
That's why we're going to run
IN the Breeders' Cup.

01:02:37.520 --> 01:02:39.560 line:83% align:left position:26% size:54%
BALON: Whoa-ho!

01:02:39.640 --> 01:02:41.520 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
MANOLIN: That sounds delicious.

01:02:41.600 --> 01:02:45.040 line:77% align:right size:80% position:90%
Well, you know, you can't just
show up with your horse

01:02:45.120 --> 01:02:46.520 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
at the Breeders' Cup, honey,

01:02:46.600 --> 01:02:48.840 line:77% align:left position:22% size:58%
<c.black>....</c>and say, "Hey, I'm here.
I wanna run in the Classic."

01:02:48.920 --> 01:02:51.160 line:77% align:left position:28% size:52%
It doesn't work that way.
<c.black>.......</c>It'd be nice if it did.

01:02:51.400 --> 01:02:52.960 line:77% align:middle position:50% size:80%
Do you know what
the selection process is?

01:02:53.040 --> 01:02:57.760 line:77% align:right size:80% position:90%
Uh...14 horses. First seven
or greatest Stakes wins, points.

01:02:57.840 --> 01:03:01.400 line:77% align:left position:26% size:54%
<c.black>.......</c>Last seven are...
No. No. I don't, really.

01:03:01.480 --> 01:03:03.840 line:77% align:left position:16% size:64%
The last seven are based on
overall performance during the year.

01:03:03.920 --> 01:03:06.200 line:77% align:left position:16% size:64%
But they do have the ability
to make a judgment call.

01:03:06.240 --> 01:03:08.160 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
I might take a shot.

01:03:08.240 --> 01:03:11.520 line:77% align:left position:16% size:64%
It's a long shot
but why not Sonador?

01:03:13.120 --> 01:03:14.520 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
Why not us?

01:03:14.600 --> 01:03:16.280 line:77% align:left position:18% size:62%
MANOLIN: Why not? That's right.
<c.black>.......................</c>LILLY: Yeah!

01:03:16.360 --> 01:03:18.760 line:77% align:left position:16% size:64%
BALON: Well, we're going
to the Breeders' Cup!

01:03:19.880 --> 01:03:22.440 line:77% align:left position:16% size:64%
LILLY: Did you really not know how
the last seven horses were chosen?

01:03:22.520 --> 01:03:25.560 line:77% align:right size:80% position:90%
No, I didn't. Why would I?
I've never been there.

01:03:25.640 --> 01:03:28.040 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
But if Sonya does get in,

01:03:28.120 --> 01:03:31.680 line:77% align:right size:80% position:90%
I can tell you there's gonna be
huge fees for a race like that, so...

01:03:31.800 --> 01:03:33.920 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
..you know, this is a pipedream.

01:03:34.000 --> 01:03:36.600 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
Remember dreams, Ben?

01:03:39.600 --> 01:03:41.320 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
This one's Cale's.

01:03:41.400 --> 01:03:43.400 line:77% align:left position:18% size:62%
Help her live it.
<c.black>....................</c>I want to, Lil.

01:03:43.520 --> 01:03:44.880 line:83% align:left position:52% size:28%
I do.

01:03:44.960 --> 01:03:48.520 line:77% align:right size:80% position:90%
I'm just saying that
this isn't gonna happen, that's all.

01:03:48.600 --> 01:03:50.000 line:83% align:left position:26% size:54%
So what?

01:03:50.080 --> 01:03:51.480 line:83% align:left position:22% size:58%
So what?

01:03:51.560 --> 01:03:53.960 line:77% align:left position:16% size:64%
Just let it take her
as far as it can.

01:03:57.120 --> 01:03:58.560 line:83% align:left position:38% size:42%
Alright.

01:03:59.560 --> 01:04:01.120 line:83% align:middle position:50% size:80%
( GALLOPING )

01:04:03.240 --> 01:04:04.680 line:83% align:left position:48% size:32%
( BEEP )

01:04:05.760 --> 01:04:07.480 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
Five furlongs in 1:01 and change.

01:04:07.560 --> 01:04:09.240 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
(Sighs) Well, that's better but...

01:04:09.320 --> 01:04:10.720 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
She was breezing, Dad.

01:04:10.840 --> 01:04:12.240 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
Don't worry.

01:04:22.320 --> 01:04:23.720 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
BEN: Mmm. Perfect.

01:04:24.000 --> 01:04:25.360 line:77% align:left position:30% size:50%
These are good.
<c.black>.................</c>(Mumbles)

01:04:27.720 --> 01:04:29.120 line:77% align:left position:16% size:64%
<c.black>................</c>CALE: Mmm.
Hey, guys.

01:04:29.200 --> 01:04:32.000 line:77% align:left position:16% size:64%
Oh, wow.
You guys got my favourite.

01:04:33.840 --> 01:04:35.280 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
Balon, where's mine?

01:04:39.160 --> 01:04:40.560 line:83% align:left position:72% size:8%
Yummy.

01:04:40.640 --> 01:04:42.040 line:83% align:left position:32% size:48%
Yay.

01:04:42.120 --> 01:04:43.960 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
Your water.

01:04:44.040 --> 01:04:45.440 line:77% align:left position:18% size:62%
This is an orange.
<c.black>...........................</c>Mm-hm.

01:04:45.520 --> 01:04:48.360 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
It looks like a painted golf ball.

01:04:48.440 --> 01:04:50.760 line:77% align:right size:80% position:90%
Hey, Manny, run her real close
to the rail, eh?

01:04:50.840 --> 01:04:52.440 line:77% align:left position:26% size:54%
You're doing good, Manny.
<c.black>..</c>You're doing real good.

01:04:52.520 --> 01:04:53.920 line:77% align:left position:56% size:24%
<c.black>.....</c>Oh, man!
Oh!

01:04:54.000 --> 01:04:56.800 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
Oh, no! No. Here, backup.

01:04:56.880 --> 01:04:59.840 line:77% align:left position:38% size:42%
CALE: Oh!
BALON: Aren't you lucky?

01:05:01.160 --> 01:05:02.720 line:83% align:left position:46% size:34%
Good girl. Yes.

01:05:02.800 --> 01:05:04.560 line:83% align:middle position:50% size:80%
Come on. Come on, Sonya.

01:05:08.480 --> 01:05:09.920 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
BEN: Cale.

01:05:12.360 --> 01:05:13.840 line:83% align:middle position:50% size:80%
I'm up. I'm up.

01:05:14.000 --> 01:05:17.200 line:83% align:middle position:50% size:80%
( MAJESTIC MUSIC )

01:05:35.680 --> 01:05:39.920 line:77% align:left position:18% size:62%
MAN: But, sir, my horse Rapidcat
is the son of Stormcat -

01:05:40.000 --> 01:05:41.440 line:83% align:middle position:50% size:80%
the best sire in the world.

01:05:41.520 --> 01:05:43.440 line:77% align:left position:30% size:50%
He deserves to run
in the Breeders' Cup.

01:05:43.520 --> 01:05:46.760 line:77% align:right size:80% position:90%
Mr Sadir Abal,
Rapidcat is 18th on the point list.

01:05:46.840 --> 01:05:50.400 line:77% align:left position:16% size:64%
<c.black>................</c>We've got 14 spots.
There's not much hope for Rapidcat.

01:05:50.480 --> 01:05:51.880 line:83% align:middle position:50% size:80%
Next.

01:05:51.960 --> 01:05:54.920 line:83% align:middle position:50% size:80%
( MURMURING )

01:05:58.360 --> 01:06:00.720 line:83% align:middle position:50% size:80%
Is Mr Cale Crane here?

01:06:00.800 --> 01:06:02.360 line:83% align:left position:30% size:50%
I'm Cale Crane.

01:06:02.480 --> 01:06:03.840 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
Why don't you stand up?

01:06:03.920 --> 01:06:05.520 line:83% align:middle position:50% size:80%
( LAUGHTER )

01:06:07.720 --> 01:06:09.560 line:83% align:middle position:50% size:80%
Miss Cale Crane.

01:06:11.400 --> 01:06:14.520 line:77% align:right size:80% position:90%
Well, Miss, your horse Sonador
has 20 points.

01:06:14.600 --> 01:06:16.440 line:77% align:right size:80% position:90%
And that puts her at 16th
on the list.

01:06:16.560 --> 01:06:19.080 line:77% align:right size:80% position:90%
Although I see that last year,
she had 42 points.

01:06:19.160 --> 01:06:20.560 line:83% align:middle position:50% size:80%
Yes, sir.

01:06:20.640 --> 01:06:23.080 line:77% align:left position:16% size:64%
She'd have that many points
this year except she was injured.

01:06:23.200 --> 01:06:24.560 line:83% align:left position:52% size:28%
She was injured?

01:06:24.640 --> 01:06:26.920 line:77% align:right size:80% position:90%
Well, do you have a vet's report
says she's sound?

01:06:27.040 --> 01:06:28.680 line:83% align:left position:30% size:50%
Right here, sir.

01:06:30.920 --> 01:06:32.320 line:77% align:left position:32% size:48%
<c.black>..............</c>Thank you.
You're welcome.

01:06:32.400 --> 01:06:34.560 line:77% align:right size:80% position:90%
You know, there are 14 horses
that get to run.

01:06:37.120 --> 01:06:39.080 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
And your horse has got a shot.

01:06:39.200 --> 01:06:41.480 line:77% align:right size:80% position:90%
But to enter this horse
in this race,

01:06:41.600 --> 01:06:44.640 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
there's gonna be a fee of £40,000.

01:06:46.800 --> 01:06:48.560 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
Did you bring a cheque?

01:06:50.200 --> 01:06:52.480 line:77% align:left position:24% size:56%
I mailed it.
<c.black>....</c>( LAUGHTER )

01:06:54.160 --> 01:06:55.880 line:83% align:left position:30% size:50%
Today.

01:06:56.000 --> 01:06:57.520 line:83% align:middle position:50% size:80%
( LAUGHTER )

01:06:57.600 --> 01:06:59.360 line:77% align:right size:80% position:90%
Well, let's just say that
the panel determines

01:06:59.400 --> 01:07:01.440 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
that Sonador belongs in this race.

01:07:01.520 --> 01:07:05.720 line:77% align:right size:80% position:90%
Now, there's another £80,000 in fees
that are gonna be due on October 26.

01:07:05.840 --> 01:07:07.720 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
Are you prepared for that?

01:07:07.800 --> 01:07:11.080 line:77% align:left position:18% size:62%
PALMER: She'll mail it to you.
<c.black>........</c>( LAUGHTER )

01:07:13.080 --> 01:07:14.480 line:83% align:left position:22% size:58%
Yes, sir. I am.

01:07:14.560 --> 01:07:17.320 line:77% align:right size:80% position:90%
Final selection will be
at 11am tomorrow.

01:07:25.520 --> 01:07:27.120 line:77% align:left position:18% size:62%
Have we got a deal?
<c.black>............</c>We've got a deal.

01:07:27.200 --> 01:07:28.640 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
Pleasure doing business with you.

01:07:36.040 --> 01:07:37.680 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
(Lilly chuckles)

01:07:41.520 --> 01:07:44.360 line:77% align:left position:16% size:64%
My knight in shining armour
has come to rescue me?

01:07:45.800 --> 01:07:47.720 line:77% align:left position:18% size:62%
'Bye. I'm gonna take off.
<c.black>....................</c>PAT: Alright.

01:07:47.800 --> 01:07:49.720 line:77% align:left position:18% size:62%
We'll see you tomorrow.
<c.black>..............</c>PAT: See you later.

01:07:49.800 --> 01:07:51.200 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
Is Cale with Pop?

01:07:51.280 --> 01:07:53.720 line:77% align:right size:80% position:90%
Yeah. They're going over
race strategies.

01:07:53.800 --> 01:07:56.520 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
Oh, she didn't get in?

01:07:56.600 --> 01:07:58.040 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
Selection's in the morning.

01:08:02.240 --> 01:08:04.160 line:77% align:right size:80% position:90%
How did Cale do
in front of the committee?

01:08:04.240 --> 01:08:05.800 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
The truth? It was rough.

01:08:05.880 --> 01:08:07.960 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
She got kicked around pretty good.

01:08:08.040 --> 01:08:09.440 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
Why are you smiling?

01:08:09.520 --> 01:08:11.360 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
Because she kicked right back.

01:08:12.800 --> 01:08:14.360 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
Yeah, she reminds me of somebody.

01:08:14.440 --> 01:08:15.840 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
(Chuckles)

01:08:15.920 --> 01:08:17.480 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
You were right, Lil.

01:08:17.560 --> 01:08:19.840 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
It was great just letting her try.

01:08:21.960 --> 01:08:23.520 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
So you're saying that I'm smart?

01:08:23.600 --> 01:08:26.200 line:77% align:right size:80% position:90%
I'm saying you're smart
and beautiful.

01:08:28.920 --> 01:08:30.840 line:77% align:left position:16% size:64%
You think she has
a chance of getting in.

01:08:30.920 --> 01:08:32.320 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
There's a chance.

01:08:32.400 --> 01:08:35.480 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
And the entry fees are £120,000, OK?

01:08:37.880 --> 01:08:39.320 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
Did you hear me?

01:08:40.840 --> 01:08:42.760 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
(Chuckles) Why are you smiling?

01:08:44.000 --> 01:08:45.960 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
I feel like I'm on a date.

01:08:58.280 --> 01:08:59.800 line:83% align:middle position:50% size:80%
BEN: Cale?

01:08:59.880 --> 01:09:01.560 line:83% align:middle position:50% size:80%
Time for bed, honey.

01:09:03.720 --> 01:09:06.680 line:77% align:left position:16% size:64%
That works a little better
than a bucket, now, doesn't it?

01:09:07.760 --> 01:09:09.800 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
(Chuckles) Yes.

01:09:13.000 --> 01:09:15.360 line:77% align:right size:80% position:90%
So how much are you gonna bet on
Sonador winning the Classic?

01:09:20.480 --> 01:09:22.240 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
Don't you think she can win?

01:09:24.280 --> 01:09:26.520 line:77% align:left position:18% size:62%
Well...
<c.black>....</c>You've gotta think she can win.

01:09:26.600 --> 01:09:28.440 line:77% align:right size:80% position:90%
What's the harm
in thinking she can win?

01:09:28.520 --> 01:09:30.640 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
Say "I think she can win".

01:09:30.720 --> 01:09:32.120 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
I think she can win.

01:09:32.200 --> 01:09:33.600 line:83% align:left position:72% size:8%
Good.

01:09:33.680 --> 01:09:36.640 line:83% align:right size:80% position:90%
She needs to hear you say that.

01:09:45.200 --> 01:09:47.800 line:77% align:left position:16% size:64%
I would like to see you run
against those boys.

01:09:56.680 --> 01:09:59.040 line:77% align:middle position:50% size:80%
MAN: May I have your attention,
please?

01:09:59.120 --> 01:10:00.520 line:83% align:middle position:50% size:80%
As chairman of the Breeders' Cup,

01:10:00.600 --> 01:10:02.520 line:83% align:middle position:50% size:80%
I am proud to announce the field

01:10:02.600 --> 01:10:05.880 line:77% align:middle position:50% size:80%
for the 22nd running
of the Breeders' Cup Classic.

