we're dropping out of the race.

01:16:57.920 --> 01:16:59.360 line:83% align:left position:38% size:42%
Oh.

01:17:01.960 --> 01:17:04.080 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
I had a dream last night, Cale.

01:17:05.760 --> 01:17:07.720 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
I was on a horse...

01:17:09.120 --> 01:17:10.600 line:83% align:left position:18% size:62%
