01:18:40.160 --> 01:18:42.600 line:77% align:left position:28% size:52%
<c.black>....</c>Morning.
Appreciate you taking my call.

01:18:45.000 --> 01:18:46.680 line:83% align:left position:24% size:56%
£120,000.

